INSERT INTO `cambridge_listening_item` VALUES (1,1,'早上好。',101400,'Good morning.',1,100192),(2,1,'欣奇布鲁克郊野公园，我是莎莉。',104920,'Hinchingbrooke Country Park,Sally speaking.',1,101402),(3,1,'我是这里的一名护林员。',106190,'I''m one of the rangers.',1,104927),(4,1,'哦,你好。',108230,'Oh hello.',1,106195),(5,1,'我叫约翰·查普曼，是当地一所小学的助教。',114270,'My name''s John Chapman,and I''m a teaching assistant at a local primary school.',1,108235),(6,1,'我受托安排我们两个班级去公园参观。',118191,'I''ve been asked to arrange a visit to the park for two of our classes.',1,114273),(7,1,'好的。',119527,'OK.',1,118192),(8,1,'您想了解些什么？',121984,'What would you like to know?',1,119553),(9,1,'嗯，我刚到这个地区，能否先介绍一下公园的情况？',128867,'Well, I''m new to this area, so perhaps you could tell me something about the park first, please.',1,121984),(10,1,'当然可以。',130118,'Of course.',1,128867),(11,1,'整个公园占地170英亩，也就是69公顷。',137245,'Altogether the park covers 170 acres, that''s 69(Q1) hectares.',1,130118),(12,1,'主要有三种生境类型:湿地、草地和林地。',143627,'There are three main types of habitat wetland,grassland and woodland.',1,137245),(13,1,'这里的树林已经形成了良好的生态环境，种类繁多，有一个橡树种植园，还有其他混合物种的区域。',151100,'The woods are well established and varied, with an oak plantation, and other areas of mixed species.',1,143627),(14,1,'是的。',152140,'Right.',1,151100),(15,1,'湿地也是多种多样的。',155061,'The wetland is quite varied, too.',1,152140),(16,1,'大约40年前，这片农田被挖掘出来提取砾石。',161097,'The original farmland was dug up around 40 years ago to extract gravel.',1,155061),(17,1,'这项工作完成后，砾石坑里灌满了水，形成了两个大湖。',168219,'Once this work was completed, the gravel pits filled with water, forming the two large lakes.',1,161097),(18,1,'还有几个较小的，池塘和一条流过公园的小溪。',175398,'There are also several smaller ones, ponds and a stream(Q2) that flows through the park.',1,168219),(19,1,'好的，所以我想在这些不同的栖息地有各种各样的野生动物。',182748,'OK, so l suppose with these different habitats there''s quite a variety of wildlife.',1,175398),(20,1,'当然有很多不同种类的鸟类和昆虫，还有鹿和兔子等动物。',192261,'There certainly is a lot of different species of birds and insects, and also animals like deer and rabbits.',1,182748),(21,1,'我了解到你们为学校团体组织教育参观活动。',197215,'And I understand you organise educational visits for school parties.',1,192261),(22,1,'这是正确的。',198668,'That''s right.',1,197215),(23,1,'我们可以组织各种活动，并根据不同年龄段进行调整。',204821,'We can organise a wide range of activities and adapt them to suit all ages.',1,198668),(24,1,'您能给我举一些活动的例子吗？',208299,'Can you give me some examples of the activities?',1,204821),(25,1,'嗯，一个重点是科学，我们帮助孩子们发现和研究植物、树木和昆虫。',216902,'Well, one focus is on science, where we help children to discover and study plants, trees and insects.',1,208299),(26,1,'他们还收集和分析他们所看到的事物的数据。',222374,'They also collect and analyse data(Q3) about the things they see.',1,216902),(27,1,'嗯嗯。',222884,'Uhuh.',1,222374),(28,1,'另一个重点是地理位置。',225777,'Another focus is on geography.',1,222884),(29,1,'公园是一个非常适合学习和练习看地图及使用指南针导航的好地方。',234759,'The park is a great environment to learn and practise reading a map(Q4) and using a compass to navigate around the park.',1,225777),(30,1,'你们有与历史相关的活动吗？',238859,'Do you do anything connected with history?',1,234759),(31,1,'是的, 我们有。',240042,'Yes,we do.',1,238859),(32,1,'例如，孩子们可以探索土地的使用是如何随着时间而变化的。',246700,'For instance, the children can explore how the use of the land has changed over time.',1,240042),(33,1,'然后是休闲和旅游。',249159,'Then there''s leisure and tourism.',1,246700),(34,1,'我猜这是针对你们的游客的，对吧？',253455,'That focuses on your visitors(Q5), I would imagine.',1,249159),(35,1,'是的,大部分是。',254750,'Yes, mostly.',1,253455),(36,1,'孩子们会了解游客的需求、可能引发的问题以及我们如何应对这些问题。',262853,'The children find out about them, their requirements, the problems they may cause and how we manage these.',1,254750),(37,1,'另一个主题是音乐：在这里，孩子们用自然材料创造声音，探索节奏和速度。',274649,'And another subject we cover is music: here the children experiment with natural materials to create sounds(Q6) and explore rhythm and tempo.',1,262853),(38,1,'那一定很有趣!',276366,'That must be fun!',1,274649),(39,1,'大多数孩子都很喜欢。',278889,'Most children really enjoy it.',1,276366),(40,1,'当然，所有的活动都是有教育意义的。',319570,'And of course, all the activities are educational, too.',1,314852),(41,1,'课外学习鼓励孩子们发挥创造力，自主探索和发现。',328228,'Learning outside the classroom encourages children to be creative, and to explore and discover for themselves.',1,319570),(42,1,'我想他们会感受到一种平时生活中不常有的自由感。',334145,'I would imagine they get a sense of freedom(Q7) that might not be a normal part of their lives.',1,328228),(43,1,'这是正确的。',335606,'That''s right.',1,334145),(44,1,'孩子们经常会发现他们可以做一些他们以前不知道自己能做的事情，他们会发展新的技能。',344418,'And very often the children discover that they can do things they didn''t know they could do, and they develop new skills(Q8).',1,335606),(45,1,'这增强了他们的自信心。',347520,'This gives them greater self-confidence.',1,344418),(46,1,'听起来不错。',349052,'It sounds great.',1,347520),(47,1,'那么，实际方面呢?',353679,'So, what about the practical side of it?',1,349052),(48,1,'一整天的参观费用是多少？',357081,'How much does it cost for a full-day visit?',1,353679),(49,1,'我们预计会带30到40个孩子来。',362181,'We would expect to bring between 30 and 40 children.',1,357081),(50,1,'如果超过30个孩子，每个孩子的费用是4.95欧元。',370134,'If there are over 30, it costs £4.95(Q9) for each child who attends on the day.',1,362181),(51,1,'我们会在活动后开具发票，这样你就不用为那些因病无法来的孩子付费。',377489,'We invoice you afterwards, so you don''t pay for children who can''t come because of sickness, for example.',1,370134),(52,1,'带队老师和其他成年人是免费的，你们可以带任意数量的成年人。',383982,'There''s no charge for leaders(Q10) and other adults as many as you want to bring.',1,377489),(53,1,'听起来很公平。',385883,'That sounds very fair.',1,383982),(54,1,'谢谢你提供的所有信息。',389169,'Well, thanks for all the information.',1,385883),(55,1,'我需要和同事们讨论一下，希望能尽快回复你并进行预订。',395130,'I''ll need to discuss it with my colleagues, and I hope to get back to you soon to make a booking.',1,389169),(56,1,'我们期待着你的消息。',397591,'We''ll look forward to hearing from you.',1,395130),(57,1,'再见。',398927,'Goodbye.',1,397591),(58,1,'再见，谢谢你。',401394,'Goodbye, and thank you.',1,398927),(59,2,'很高兴今晚能在这里见到这么多友好协会的成员。',68499,'It''s great to see so many members of the Twinning Association here tonight.',1,62883),(60,2,'自从英国的斯坦索普和法国的马拉特建立结对关系以来，两镇的关系日益密切。',83320,'Since the twinning link between our two towns, Stanthorpe here in England and Malatte in France, was established, the relationship between the towns has gone from strength to strength.',1,68499),(61,2,'上个月，来自斯坦索普的25名协会成员在马拉特度过了一个周末。',91160,'Last month, 25 members of the association from Stanthorpe spent a weekend in Malatte.',1,83321),(62,2,'我们的东道主安排了一个很棒的活动。',94501,'Our hosts had arranged a great programme.',1,91169),(63,2,'我们了解了该地区如何生产奶酪，并有机会品尝产品。',101094,'We learned how cheese is produced in the region and had the chance to taste the products.',1,94501),(64,2,'主题公园之旅不得不取消，但我们在最后的河上游船之旅中玩得很开心，那才是真正的亮点。',112100,'The theme park trip had to be cancelled, but we all had a great time on the final boat trip down the river, that was the real highlight.(Q11)',1,101094),(65,2,'今年对协会来说是特别的一年，因为我们已经成立了25年。',119661,'This is a special year for the Association because it''s 25 years since we were founded.',1,112101),(66,2,'在马拉特，他们计划通过在市政公园建造一座人行桥来纪念这一时刻。',126925,'In Malatte, they''re planning to mark this by building a footbridge in the municipal park.',1,119661),(67,2,'我们一直在讨论如何纪念这个时刻，最后决定在博物馆花园里种一棵白杨树。',135381,'We''ve been discussing what to do here and we ''ve decided to plant a poplar tree in the museum gardens.(Q12)',1,126925),(68,2,'我们考虑过买一个花园座椅放在那里，但相关部门不赞同这个想法。',142363,'We considered buying a garden seat to put there, but the authorities weren''t happy with that idea.',1,135381),(69,2,'在筹款支持我们的活动方面，我们做得很成功。',148959,'In terms of fundraising to support our activities, we''ve done very well.',1,142363),(70,2,'我们的煎饼之夜非常成功，创下了利润新高。',155142,'Our pancake evening was well attended and made record profits.(Q13)',1,148959),(71,2,' 大家都很喜欢法式烹饪的展示，几乎同样成功。',161742,'And everyone enjoyed the demonstration of French cookery, which was nearly as successful.',1,155142),(72,2,'由于场地限制，我们的电影放映人数有限，所以明年我们会寻找更大的场地。',170300,'Numbers for our film show were limited because of the venue so we''re looking for