 less is known about the effects of microplastics in freshwater and particularly in soil.',1,92822),(588,12,'微塑料可以通过多种途径进入环境。',113433,'Microplastics can enter the environment via a number of different sources.',1,106405),(589,12,'每次将合成纤维衣物放入洗衣机时，线头和微纤维就会脱落并进入水系统。',124083,'Threads and microfibres detach from synthetic clothing(Q31) every time they''re put in a washing machine, and these find their way into the water system.',1,113433),(590,12,'其他来源包括已经存在于环境中的大块塑料垃圾，这些垃圾会在一段时间内分解成微小颗粒。',135858,'Other sources include big pieces of plastic waste that are already in the environment, and these break down into microscopic particles over a period of time.',1,124083),(591,12,'在更大范围内，工厂废料和汽车、卡车等在路面行驶时磨损的轮胎也是微塑料的来源。',148427,'On a larger scale, factory waste is another route, as are tyres which wear down as cars, lorries and so on travel along road surfaces.',1,135858),(592,12,'通过对鱼类和其他动物的研究，我们已经了解了一些微塑料的影响。',157354,'We already understand some of the impacts of microplastics from studies involving fish and other animals.',1,148427),(593,12,'有证据表明，微塑料会以多种方式伤害小型生物，比如损害它们的口腔，或影响它们的进食能力，例如微塑料滞留在它们的消化系统中。',174733,'There is evidence that microplastics harm small creatures in a variety of ways, such as by damaging their mouths(Q32), or by impairing their ability to feed, for example when microplastics get lodged in their digestive system.',1,157354),(594,12,'令人惊讶的是，人类很可能会摄入微塑料，因为在包括瓶装水在内的各种食品和饮料产品中，甚至在自来水中，都检测到了微塑料。',190079,'Surprisingly perhaps, it is likely that humans consume microplastics, as these have been detected in a wide range of food and drink products, including bottled water, as well as in water that comes direct from the tap.',1,174733),(595,12,'更重要的是，盐和许多种类的海鲜也被发现含有微塑料。',197437,'What''s more, salt(Q33) and many kinds of seafood have also been found to contain microplastics.',1,190079),(596,12,'然而，需要强调的是，目前还没有确凿的证据表明微塑料会对人体造成重大伤害。',207273,'However, it''s important to underline that there is not yet conclusive proof that microplastics cause significant harm to people.',1,197437),(597,12,'在许多国家，包括英国，都有法律禁止制造商在沐浴露、洗面奶和牙膏中添加塑料微珠。',217846,'In many countries, including here in the UK, there is legislation which prevents manufacturers from adding plastic microbeads to shower gels, facial cleansers and toothpaste.',1,207273),(598,12,'洗面奶和牙膏中添加塑料微珠。',220897,'facial cleansers and toothpaste(Q34).',1,217846),(599,12,'由于土壤中的塑料微粒很难检测到，因此很难准确估计它们的总量，但我们确实知道它们在空气中被携带，并通过雨水沉积在土壤中。',236578,'It is very difficult to accurately estimate the total amount of microplastic particles in the soil as they can be hard to detect, but we do know they are carried in the air and deposited in the soil by rain.',1,220897),(600,12,'更重要的是，农民和园丁使用的许多肥料都含有微塑料。',244755,'What''s more, many of the fertilisers(Q35) used by both farmers and gardeners contain microplastics.',1,236578),(601,12,'剑桥安格利亚鲁斯金大学的一个研究小组进行了一项关于微塑料对蚯蚓消化道影响的研究。',259070,'A team from the Anglia Ruskin University in Cambridge has carried out a study of the effects of microplastics on the digestive tracts of earthworms.',1,249800),(602,12,'这些生活在表土中的蠕虫是我们农业系统的重要组成部分。',266900,'These worms, which live in topsoil, are an essential component of our agricultural system.',1,259070),(603,12,'它们通过食用土壤，将养分混合其中，从而使其更加肥沃。',274528,'By feeding on soil, they mix nutrients(Q36) into it, thereby making it more fertile.',1,266900),(604,12,'研究人员着手发现，将微塑料引入土壤，以及随后蚯蚓对这些塑料的摄入是否会影响土壤质量，并最终抑制植物生长。',288891,'The researchers set out to discover whether the introduction of microplastics into the soil -and the subsequent ingestion of these by earthworms would impact soil quality and ultimately Inhibit plant growth(Q37).',1,274528),(605,12,'简短的回答是，是的，确实如此。',291858,'The short answer was, yes, it did.',1,288891),(606,12,'在土壤中放入三种不同类型的微塑料颗粒后，他们种植了多年生黑麦草。',299494,'After placing three different types of microplastic particles into the soil, they planted perennial rye grass.',1,291858),(607,12,'这些塑料微粒包括可生物降解的聚乳酸(PLA)和传统的高密度聚乙烯(HDPE)，然后被土壤中的蚯蚓摄入。',311609,'The particles of microplastic, which included biodegradable PLA and conventional high-de