385),(903,17,'你用过吗?',332190,'Do you ever use those?',1,330766),(904,17,'不，我不喜欢骑自行车去那里，因为污染太严重了。',337760,'No – I’m not keen on cycling there because of all the pollution(Q9).',1,332195),(905,17,'但我想要一辆自行车，骑自行车去上班会很好',343050,'But I would like to get a bike – it would be good to use it to get to work.',1,337763),(906,17,'那你为什么现在还没有呢?',345340,'So why haven’t you got one now?',1,343053),(907,17,'嗯，我住在一套公寓里，在二楼，没有任何储物空间，所以我们必须把它放在公寓外面的大厅里。',356470,'Well, I live in a flat – on the second floor and it doesn’t have any storage(Q10) – so we’d have to leave it in the hall outside the flat.',1,345341),(908,17,'我明白了。',357330,'I see.',1,356476),(909,17,'好的。',358650,'OK.',1,357331),(910,17,'嗯，我想就这些了。',361559,'Well, I think that’s all ..',1,358656),(911,18,'大家晚上好。',59040,'Good evening, everyone.',1,56986),(912,18,'首先，我欢迎大家参加这次演讲，并感谢大家抽出时间考虑加入ACE志愿组织。',68450,'Let me start by welcoming you all to this talk and thanking you for taking the time to consider joining ACE voluntary organisation.',1,59049),(913,18,'ACE为当地的人们和服务提供支持，我们现在正在寻找更多的志愿者来帮助我们做这件事。',77830,'ACE offers support to people and services in the local area and we’re now looking for more volunteers to help us do this.',1,68451),(914,18,'顺便说一下，我希望你们都很舒服。我们增加了额外的座位，大家不需要站着，但这就代表在房间后面的人可能会有点拥挤。',89590,'By the way, I hope you’re all comfortable – we have brought in extra seats so that no one has to stand, but it does mean that the people at the back of the room may be a bit squashed.(Q11)',1,77831),(915,18,'我们只会在这里待半个小时，希望你们不会介意。',94500,'We’ll only be here for about half an hour so, hopefully, that’s OK.',1,89591),(916,18,'我们经常被问到的第一个问题是，你需要多大年龄才能成为志愿者。',101170,'One of the first questions we’re often asked is how old you need to be to volunteer.',1,94509),(917,18,'你可能只有16岁，也可能60岁以上;这完全取决于你想做什么类型的志愿工作。',110550,'Well, you can be as young as 16 or you can be 60 or over(Q12); it all depends on what type of voluntary work you want to do.',1,101178),(918,18,'其他考虑因素，比如可靠性，在志愿工作中是至关重要的，而根据我们的经验，年龄与这些无关。',121060,'Other considerations, such as reliability, are crucial(Q12) in voluntary work and age isn’t related to these, in our experience.',1,110555),(919,18,'我们被问到的另一个问题与培训有关。',125240,'Another question we get asked relates to training.',1,121069),(920,18,'有很多这样的机会，而且都是面对面的。',130030,'Well, there’s plenty of that and it’s all face-to-face.',1,125244),(921,18,'更重要的是，你为我们工作的时候，培训并不会结束。一般会在工作之前，工作期间和工作之后进行培训。',139030,'What’s more, training doesn’t end when you start working for us – it takes place before, during and after periods of work.(Q13)',1,130037),(922,18,'通常，其他有经验的志愿者负责培训，因为经理往往更喜欢处理其他事情。',146420,'Often, it’s run by other experienced volunteers as managers tend to prefer to get on with other things.',1,139037),(923,18,'在你决定申请志愿工作之前，我想请你考虑几个重要的问题。',154940,'Now, I would ask you to consider a couple of important issues before you decide to apply for voluntary work.',1,146427),(924,18,'我们不在意您想成为一名志愿者的原因。人们有很多不同的理由，有的人想要获得工作经验，也有的人说这只是做了他们一直想做的事情。',167630,'We don’t worry about why you want to be a volunteer – people have many different reasons that range from getting work experience to just doing something they’ve always wanted to do.',1,154949),(925,18,'但最重要的是，你每天要有足够的时间来做我们认为适合你的工作——如果做志愿者让你感到压力很大，那么最好不要做志愿者。',180710,'But it is critical that you have enough hours in the day(Q14)(Q15) for whatever role we agree is suitable for you – if being a volunteer becomes stressful then it’s best not to do it at all.',1,167638),(926,18,'你可能认为你的收入很重要，但我们不会问这个问题。',185980,'You may think that your income is important, but we don’t ask about that.',1,180719),(927,18,'你是否可以不挣钱而工作，这取决于你自己。',190170,'It’s up to you to decide if you can work without earning money.',1,185986),(928,18,'我们看重的是奉献精神。',193080,'What we value is dedication.(Q14)(Q15)',1,190171),(929,18,'我们的一些最忠诚的志愿者自己挣得很少，但他们仍然为我们的工作付出了全部的精力。',241860,'Some of our most loyal volunteers earn very little themselves but still give their full energy to the work they do with us.',1,193081),(930,18,'好，让我们聊聊需要志愿者的一些工作领域以及可以在这些领域给大家的帮助。',250550,'OK, so let’s take a look