ecies of moths. I''d enjoy that.',1,190713),(1668,33,'我们在保护区做的另一项工作是更换南侧的墙壁，在停车场和我们的木棚之间。它在上个月的暴风雨中严重受损。',209950,'Another job we''re doing at the reserve is replacing the wall on the southern side, between the parking area and our woodshed. It was badly damaged in a storm last month.(Q5)',1,199222),(1669,33,'好的。',251350,'OK.',1,209951),(1670,33,'然后，正如我所说，我们也有一个活动计划，包括周末和工作日。',257670,'Then as I said, we have a programme of events as well, both at the weekend, and during the week.',1,251356),(1671,33,'没错。我想你有引导步行？',261980,'Right. I presume you have guided walks?',1,257676),(1672,33,'我想了解当地的乡村，因为我是该地区的新手。',266560,'I''d like to get to know the local countryside, as I''m new to the area.',1,261985),(1673,33,'是的，我们有。接下来的步行是周六的一周去拉斯顿岛。',271540,'Yes, we do. The next walk is to Ruston Island, a week on Saturday.',1,266567),(1674,33,'我们将在退潮时在邓斯莫尔海滩的停车场见面——那时沙子足够干燥，我们可以步行到岛上而不会被淋湿。',280310,'We''ll be meeting in the car park at Dunsmore Beach at low tide – that''s when the sands are dry enough for us to walk to the island without getting wet.(Q6)',1,271548),(1675,33,'听起来不错。',281260,'Sounds good.',1,280319),(1676,33,'该岛是探索的好地方。',284390,'The island''s a great place to explore.',1,281265),(1677,33,'它很小，而且有各种各样的栖息地。',287400,'It''s quite small, and it''s got a range of habitats.',1,284396),(1678,33,'它也是在海岸附近甚至海滩上观赏海豹的理想地点。',293340,'It''s also an ideal location for seeing seals just off the coast, or even on the beach.',1,287407),(1679,33,'好的。有什么我们应该带的吗，比如野餐？',299660,'OK. And is there anything we should bring, like a picnic, for instance?',1,293348),(1680,33,'是的，一定要带一个，因为这是一整天的步行。',303080,'Yes, do bring one, as it''s a full-day walk.',1,299668),(1681,33,'当然，走来走去会很湿，所以要确保你的靴子是防水的。',309600,'And of course it''ll be wet walking across and back, so make sure your boots are waterproof.(Q7)',1,303089),(1682,33,'我必须买一双新的——我现在的一双有一个洞！',313820,'I must buy a new pair – there''s a hole in one of my current ones!',1,309601),(1683,33,'好吧，我肯定想来散步。',317560,'Well, I''d definitely like to come on the 