ee staff members on board and on top of that, we can transport a further fifteen people – that''s you – around the coastline.',1,77856),(1701,34,'但是请注意，如果船的两边超过九个人，我们会把你们中的一些人移过来，否则我们十八个人都会落海！',99850,'But please note if there are more than nine people on either side of the boat, we''ll move some of you over, otherwise all eighteen of us will end up in the sea!(Q11)',1,88885),(1702,34,'我们最近升级了我们所有的船。',103270,'We''ve recently upgraded all our boats.',1,99856),(1703,34,'它们曾经是黑色的，但我们的新座椅现在有这些舒适的深红色座椅和浅绿色的外观，以便从其他人中脱颖而出并帮助宣传我们的公司。',116140,'They used to be jet black, but our new ones now have these comfortable dark red seats and a light-green exterior in order to stand out from others and help promote our company.(Q12)',1,103275),(1704,34,'这给我们的船一个相当独特的外观，你不觉得吗？',120400,'This gives our boats a rather unique appearance, don''t you think?',1,116147),(1705,34,'我们在旅途中为您提供免费午餐盒，我们有三种类型。',125820,'We offer you a free lunchbox during the trip and we have three types.',1,120405),(1706,34,'午餐盒 1 包含火腿和番茄三明治。',130700,'Lunchbox 1 contains ham and tomato sandwiches.',1,125824),(1707,34,'午餐盒 2 包含切达干酪卷，午餐盒 3 以沙拉为主，还包含鸡蛋和金枪鱼。',140810,'Lunchbox 2 contains a cheddar cheese roll and Lunchbox 3 is salad-based and also contains eggs and tuna.(Q13)',1,130707),(1708,34,'所有三个午餐盒里面还有一包薯片和巧克力棒。',146880,'All three lunchboxes also have a packet of crisps and chocolate bar inside.',1,140816),(1709,34,'请让工作人员知道您喜欢哪种午餐盒。',150830,'Please let staff know which lunchbox you prefer.',1,146885),(1710,34,'我敢肯定我不必要求你不要把任何东西扔进海里。',156840,'I''m sure I don''t have to ask you not to throw anything into the sea.',1,150835),(1711,34,'我们没有任何垃圾箱可放入垃圾箱，但 Jess、我本人或我们的另一位向导 Ray 会在午餐后从您那里收集垃圾并将其全部放入一个大塑料袋中。',214900,'We don''t have any bins to put litter in, but Jess, myself or Ray, our other guide, will collect it from you after lunch and put it all in a large plastic sack.(Q14)',1,156845),(1712,34,'船上的引擎发出很大的噪音，所以在我们出发之前，让我告诉你一些关于你将要看到的事情。',223700,'The engine on the boat makes quite a lot of noise so before we head off, let me tell you a few things about what you''re going to see.',1,214908),(1713,34,'该地区以其古老的灯塔而闻名，当我们转过第一个小岛时，您会从船上看到。',231820,'This area is famous for its ancient lighthouse, which you''ll see from the boat as we turn past the first little island.',1,223708),(1714,34,'它建于1838年，因为一些船只失事导致了重大的生命损失，因此它用于保护水手。',240470,'It was built in 1838 to protect sailors as a number of shipwrecks had led to significant loss of life.(Q15)',1,231820),(1715,34,'由于地方议会保存的一些原始图纸显示，建筑本身很复杂。',248450,'The construction itself was complicated as some of the original drawings kept by the local council show.',1,240479),(1716,34,'它坐落在悬崖顶上一个非常偏僻的地方。',253540,'It sits right on top of the cliffs in a very isolated spot.',1,248457),(1717,34,'在 19 世纪，那里有许多工作，例如抛光黄铜灯、砍柴和清洁窗户，让灯塔管理员忙得不可开交。',266380,'In the nineteenth century there were many jobs there, such as polishing the brass lamps, chopping firewood and cleaning windows, that kept lighthouse keepers busy.',1,253548),(1718,34,'这些工人主要是监狱犯，直到那个世纪中叶愿意生活在这种情况下的普通家庭接管了。',277190,'These workers were mainly prison convicts until the middle of that century when ordinary families willing to live in such circumstances took over.(Q16)',1,266388),(1719,34,'你们中的一些人问我我们可以期待看到什么生物。',282250,'Some of you have asked me what creatures we can expect to see.',1,277196),(1720,34,'我知道每个人都喜欢企鹅，但它们非常害羞，不幸的是，它们往往会躲避过往的船只，但你可能会看到远处的鸟类，如海雕，在它们筑巢的悬崖边缘飞来飞去。',299150,'I know everyone loves the penguins, but they''re very shy and, unfortunately, tend to hide from passing boats, but you might see birds in the distance, such as sea eagles, flying around the cliff edges where they nest.',1,282255),(1721,34,'当我们到达海狗栖息的岩石区域时，我们会停下来观看它们在海岸周围游泳。',307900,'When we get to the rocky area inhabited by fur seals, we''ll stop and watch them swimming around the coast.(Q17)',1,299153),(1722,34,'他们是好奇的生物，所以如果有生物突然出现在你面前，不要感到惊讶。',314070,'They''re inquisitive creatures so don''t be surprised if one pops up right in front of you.',1,307903),(1723,34,'“它们的捕食者，逆戟鲸，也沿着海岸线捕猎，但发现其中一只是罕见的。”',322380,'Their pred