y, too?',1,194181),(1857,37,'我可以参与一两个，特别是如果有任何艺术团体。',205180,'I could get involved in one or two, particularly if there are any art groups.(Q5)',1,199160),(1858,37,'太棒啦。我会找出我们需要帮助的地方并回复你。',210490,'Excellent. I''ll find out where we need help and get back to you.',1,205181),(1859,37,'好的。对个别居民的帮助如何。',214890,'Fine. What about help for individual residents.',1,210491),(1860,37,'你安排好了吗？',217010,'Do you arrange that at all?',1,214891),(1861,37,'是的，我们一次性完成。',219800,'Yes, we do it as a one-off.',1,217013),(1862,37,'事实上，还有卡罗尔夫人。',223220,'In fact, there''s Mrs Carroll.',1,219803),(1863,37,'她下周需要乘车去医院，我们正在努力寻找人。',228810,'She needs a lift to the hospital next week, and we''re struggling to find someone.(Q6)',1,223221),(1864,37,'她的约会是什么时候？',230810,'When''s her appointment?',1,228813),(1865,37,'星期二。这需要整个上午。',234220,'On Tuesday. It would take the whole morning.',1,230813),(1866,37,'我可以那样做。',235710,'I could do that.',1,234224),(1867,37,'哦，那太好了。谢谢你。',238020,'Oh, that would be great. Thank you.',1,235713),(1868,37,'而且，下周，我们将安排在塞尔斯伯里先生搬家之前对他的房子进行一些工作，因为他身体不够健康，不能自己动手。',248800,'And also, next week, we''re arranging to have some work done to Mr Selsbury''s house before he moves, as he isn''t healthy enough to do it himself.',1,238020),(1869,37,'我们有一些人来装饰他的厨房，但如果你能在他的花园里除草，那就太好了。',256920,'We''ve got some people to decorate his kitchen, but if you could do some weeding in his garden(Q7), that would be wonderful.',1,248801),(1870,37,'好的。我会喜欢的。大概日期和时间是灵活的。',263280,'OK. I''d enjoy that. And presumably the day and time are flexible.',1,256921),(1871,37,'哦是的。只要说出什么时候最适合您，我们就会通知塞尔斯伯里先生。',268610,'Oh yes. Just say when would suit you best, and we''ll let Mr Selsbury know.',1,263284),(1872,37,'好的。',300160,'Good.',1,268615),(1873,37,'志愿者小组还组织每月的社交活动，当然，这是结识其他人的好方法。',308500,'The volunteers group also organises monthly social events, which is a great way to meet other people, of course.',1,300168),(1874,37,'嗯。',309380,'Uhuh.',1,308509),(1875,37,'因此，下个月，即 10 月 19 日，我们将举行一次测验——一些居民擅长计划不寻常的事情，我们总是挤满村大厅。'