ay.',1,393190),(1890,37,'酒店将提供晚餐，我们已经预订了乐队。',412690,'The hotel will be providing dinner and we''ve booked a band.',1,408235),(1891,37,'我们还没有得到一张海报。',416770,'The one thing we haven''t got yet is a poster.(Q10)',1,412693),(1892,37,'无论如何，那不是你能做的，是吗？',420240,'That isn''t something you could do, by any chance, is it?',1,416773),(1893,37,'实际上，是的。在我退休之前，我是一名平面设计师，所以那正是我的本行。',427740,'Well actually, yes. Before I retired I was a graphic designer, so that''s right up my street.',1,420243),(1894,37,'哦完美！我会给你详细信息，然后也许你可以给我发一份草稿……',433990,'Oh perfect! I''ll give you the details, and then perhaps you could send me a draft …',1,427741),(1895,37,'当然。',434970,'Of course.',1,433997),(1896,38,'早上好，欢迎来到奥尼顿庄园，这是当地最大的庄园之一',57500,'Good morning, and welcome to Oniton Hall, one of the largest estates in the area.',1,50579),(1897,38,'我叫尼克，我是其中一名导游',60730,'My name''s Nick, and I''m one of the guides.',1,57509),(1898,38,'你们坐着的时候我给你们简单介绍一下庄园的情况，然后我们再四处走走',67710,'I''ll give you a brief introduction to the estate while you''re sitting down, and then we''ll walk round.',1,60739),(1899,38,'该庄园由房屋、花园、公园和农场组成，其历史可追溯到14世纪',78020,'The estate consists of the house, gardens, parkland and farm, and it dates back to the fourteenth century.',1,67712),(1900,38,'原来的房子在17世纪后期被取代了，当然它有很多主人',86880,'The original house was replaced in the late seventeenth century, and of course it has had a large number of owners.',1,78029),(1901,38,'几乎所有的房子都留下了自己的印记，通常是增加了新的房间，比如舞厅和温室，或者拆除了其他房间',99130,'Almost all of them have left their mark, generally by adding new rooms, like the ballroom and conservatory, or by demolishing others.(Q11)',1,86883),(1902,38,'尽管现在的主人在花坛上做了大量的工作，农场看起来还是和以前一样',108680,'The farm looks much as it''s always done, although the current owner has done a great deal of work to the flower beds.',1,99133),(1903,38,'在17世纪，这个庄园属于一个非常富有的人，他叫爱德华·唐斯爵士',116880,'In the seventeenth century, the estate was owned by a very wealthy man called Sir Edward Downes.',1,108683),(1904,38,'作为一名活跃的政治家，他的意图是逃离政治世界，并建造一座新房子，以配得上他收藏