 2 percent sugar and other nutrients.',1,341844),(2390,48,'汁液需要被煮沸，只有这样做，水才能被蒸发，而且这一步需要立即使用蒸发器操作。',362060,'It has to be boiled so that much of that water evaporates, and this process has to take place immediately, using what are called evaporators.',1,351173),(2391,48,'这些基本上都是非常大的锅，把树液倒入其中，然后生火加热锅，直到树液沸腾。',374490,'These are basically extremely large pans – the sap is poured into these, a fire is built and the pans are then heated until the sap boils.(Q37)',1,362064),(2392,48,'在这个过程中，水蒸发了，糖浆开始形成。',380470,'As it does this, the water evaporates, and the syrup begins to form.',1,374497),(2393,48,'蒸发过程会产生大量的蒸汽，树液会变得更厚、更密，在合适的时刻，当树液变得足够厚，可以被称为枫糖浆时，工人把它从高温中取出。',397290,'The evaporation process creates large quantities of steam, and the sap becomes thicker and denser, and, at just the right moment, when the sap is thick enough to be called maple syrup, the worker removes it from the heat.(Q38)',1,380475),(2394,48,'在这个过程之后，需要过滤掉一种叫做“糖沙”的东西，因为在煮沸的过程中，糖沙堆积起来，使糖浆看起来浑浊，味道有点粗糙。',410390,'After this process, something called‘sugar sand'' has to be filtered out as this builds up during the boiling and gives the syrup a cloudy appearance and a slightly gritty taste.(Q39)',1,397299),(2395,48,'一旦这样做了，糖浆就准备好包装了，这样它就可以用于各种各样的产品。',418580,'Once this has been done, the syrup is ready to be packaged so that it can be used for a whole variety of products.',1,410397),(2396,48,'生产一升枫树糖浆需要40升树液，所以你可以了解到需要这多少树液！',428800,'It takes 40 litres of sap to produce one litre of maple syrup so you can get an idea of how much is needed!(Q40)',1,418584),(2397,48,'这就是基本的过程。',432700,'So that''s the basic process.',1,428806),(2398,48,'在魁北克这样的地方……',435040,'In places like Quebec where …',1,432708),(2399,49,'你好。儿童工程研讨会。',89830,'Hello.Children''s Engineering Workshops.',1,87001),(2400,49,'哦,你好。',91180,'Oh hello.',1,89831),(2401,49,'我想了解一些关于学校放假期间研讨会的信息。',95620,'I wanted some information about the workshops in the school holidays.',1,91181),(2402,49,'确定。',96600,'Sure.',1,95621),(2403,49,'我的两个女儿都很感兴趣。',99330,'I have 