nned in the park.',1,228033),(8947,182,'我们有自行车，您可以在接待区后面租用......在这里......你们中的健康人可以步行去，最后是我们的电动有轨电车，由太阳能电池供电......',246790,'We have bicycles which you can hire behind the Reception block ... here ... the healthy ones of you can go on foot and finally there''s our electric tram, powered from solar cells.（Q16）',1,234902),(8948,182,'您可以在正门找到更多相关信息。',250380,'You find more information about this at the front entrance..',1,246799),(8949,182,'稀有品种部分是您开始旅行的好地方。',254000,'A good place to start on your tour is the Rare Breeds section.',1,250386),(8950,182,'我们饲养山羊、绵羊、母鸡和其他种类的家禽。',259010,'We keep goats（Q17）, sheep and hens and other kinds of poultry.',1,254001),(8951,182,'我们也在考虑引进牛和马，但我们还没有为这些更大的动物提供设施。',266370,'We are also thinking of bringing in cows and horses but we do not, as yet, have facilities for these bigger animals.',1,259012),(8952,182,'这些动物每天在公共场所喂食两次，并就它们的摄食习惯和营养需求进行简短的讲座。',273910,'The animals are fed in public twice a day and a short lecture given on their feeding habits and nutritional needs.',1,266372),(8953,182,'这些很受公众欢迎，但我们当然不能忽视设立这个部分的主要目的，不是为了保护珍稀动物，而是为了保持品种的多样性，扩大农业发展的基因库。',290140,'These are very popular with the public but of course we mustn''t lose sight of the main purpose of having this section, not as such to preserve rare animals but to maintain the diversity of breeds（Q18） to broaden the gene pool for agricultural development.',1,273912),(8954,182,'绿谷随着季节的变化而变化，在一年中的不同时间发生不同的事件。',295670,'Green Vale changes with the seasons with different events happening at different times of the year.',1,290144),(8955,182,'随着加拿大鹅的到来，五月可能是我们最壮观的月份，届时我们的果树将盛开，但全年都有有趣的活动。',307660,'May will be perhaps our most spectacular month with the arrival of the Canada geese and when our fruit trees will be in full blossom, but there are interesting events on all year round.',1,295675),(8956,182,'例如，我们的飞蝇钓专家约翰·哈弗斯（John Havers）目前正在湖上垂钓。',315400,'for example John Havers, our expert fly fisherman, is currently giving displays on the lake.（Q19）',1,307667),(8957,182,'每个部分都有自己的季节性日历。',31