're pretty keen to make sure that there aren''t any more getting in, particularly to New South Wales and other states.',1,111333),(8968,183,'亚洲蜜蜂有什么问题？它们与澳大利亚蜜蜂有那么大的不同吗？',123990,'What''s wrong with Asian Honey Bees? Are they so different from Australian bees?',1,118889),(8969,183,'嗯，事实上，它们看起来几乎一样，但它们身上长满了螨虫——生活在它们身上的微小生物，它们会严重损害我们自己的本土蜜蜂，甚至可能消灭它们。',138150,'Well, in fact, they look almost the same, but they are infested with mites- microscopic creatures which live on them, and which can seriously damage our own home-grown bees, or could even wipe them out.（Q22）',1,123997),(8970,183,'那么，如果澳大利亚蜜蜂灭绝会发生什么？',141750,'Well, what would happen if Australian bees died out?',1,138156),(8971,183,'嗯，澳大利亚蜜蜂的蜂蜜质量上乘，比亚洲蜜蜂生产的蜂蜜要好得多。',149030,'Well, the honey from Australian bees is of excellent quality, much better than the stuff the Asian bees produce.',1,141758),(8972,183,'事实上，澳大利亚也正因为如此，将本土蜂王出口到许多国家。',155100,'In fact, Australia exports native Queen bees to a large number of countries because of this.（Q23）',1,149031),(8973,183,'当欧洲蜜蜂第一次在灌木丛中被发现时，我们发现它们制造的蜂蜜非常难闻，而且它们也太大而无法为我们在澳大利亚的许多本土花卉授粉。',167680,'When the European Honey Bee was first discovered out in the bush, we found they made really unpleasant honey and they were also too big to pollinate many of our native flowers here in Australia.',1,155109),(8974,183,'这一定对自然植物群产生了毁灭性的影响。',171700,'That must have had a devastating effect on the natural flora.',1,167681),(8975,183,'有丢失任何物种吗？',173610,'Did you lose any species?',1,171708),(8976,183,'不，我们设法在此之前控制住了它们，但如果亚洲蜜蜂进入，可能会产生其他后果。',181630,'No, we managed to get them under control before that happened but if Asian bees got in there could be other consequences.',1,173615),(8977,183,'我们可能会损失很多钱，因为您可能不知道，但据估计，本地蜜蜂为豪尔和蔬菜作物授粉的价值每年为 12 亿美元。',193780,'We could lose a lot of money （Q24）because you might not be aware, but it''s estimated that native bees'' pollination of flower and vegetable crops is worth 1.2 billion dollars a year.',1,181633),(8978,183,'所以在某种程度上，他们是农民的朋友。',196280,'So in a way they''re the farmers'' friend.',1,193781),(8979,183,'哦，另一件事是，如果亚洲蜜蜂蛰伤了你，某些人会产生过敏反应；所以它们比本地蜜蜂危险得多。',253560,'Oh, and another thing is, if you''re stung by an Asian Honey Bee, it can produce an allergic reaction in some people; so they''re much more dangerous than native bees.',1,196285),(8980,183,'您如何知道亚洲蜜蜂是否已进入澳大利亚？',256870,'How will you know if Asian bees have entered Australia?',1,253568),(8981,183,'我们正在研究一种叫做彩虹食蜂鸟的鸟的饮食。',261430,'We''re looking at the diet of the bird called the Rainbow Bee Eater.',1,256874),(8982,183,'蜂食者不在乎它吃什么，只要它们是昆虫。',265730,'The Bee Eater doesn''t care what it eats, as long as they''re insects.（Q25）',1,261437),(8983,183,'但这只鸟的有趣之处在于，我们能够准确分析它吃什么，如果我们正在寻找外来昆虫，这真的很有帮助。',274550,'But the interesting thing about this bird is that we are able to analyse exactly what it eats and that''s really helpful if we''re looking for introduced insects.',1,265739),(8984,183,'怎么会那样？',275720,'How come?',1,274557),(8985,183,'因为昆虫的骨骼在体外，所以食蜂鸟从里面消化肉。',283000,'Because insects have their skeletons outside their bodies, so the Bee Eaters digest the meat from the inside.',1,275723),(8986,183,'然后他们拿出所有难以消化的骨骼碎片，当然还有颗粒状的翅膀——他们咳出的一小团废料。',293000,'Then they bring up all the indigestible bits of skeleton and, of course, the wings in a pellet - a small ball of waste material which they cough up.',1,283001),(8987,183,'这听起来有点不愉快。那么，你怎么做呢？',296480,'That sounds a bit unpleasant. So, how do you go about it?',1,293001),(8988,183,'在野外，我们追踪食蜂鸟并找到他们最喜欢的觅食点，你知道的，这些鸟通常喂食的地方。',304000,'In the field we track down the Bee Eaters and find their favourite feeding （Q26）spots, you know, the places where the birds usually feed.',1,296481),(8989,183,'在这里，我们可以找到颗粒。',307200,'It''s here that we can find the pellets.',1,304001),(8990,183,'我们将它们收集起来并带回实验室检查内容。',311660,'We collect them up and take them back to the laboratory（Q27） to examine the contents.',1,307206),(8991,183,'你是怎样做的？',313300,'How do you do that?',1,311661),(8992,183,'颗粒真的很硬，特别是如果它们已经在阳光下晒了几天，所以首先，我们通过加水来润湿它们并使其更柔软来处理它们。',324510,'The pellets are really hard, especially if they have been out in the sun for a few days so, first of all, we treat them by adding water （Q28）to moisten them and make them softer.',1,313307),(8993,183,'然后我们在显微镜下把它们分开。',327620,'Then we pull them apart under the microscope.',1,324512),(8994,183,'一切都被卷曲了，但我们正在寻找翅膀，所以我们只是将它们全部拉出并拉直它们。',334690,'Everything''s all scrunched up but we''re looking for wings so we just pull them all out and straighten them.',1,327623),(8995,183,'然后我们识别它们，看看我们是否能找到任何亚洲蜜蜂的翅膀。',338630,'Then we identify them to see if we can find any Asian bee wings.（Q29）',1,334696),(8996,183,'你找到了多少？',340350,'And how many have you found?',1,338634),(8997,183,'到目前为止，我们的研究表明，亚洲蜜蜂还没有大量进入澳大利亚——这是一个很好的结果，而且比试图找到活的蜜蜂作为引入昆虫的证据要可靠得多。',352170,'So far our research shows that Asian bees have not entered Australia in any number - it''s a good result and much more reliable than trying to find live ones as evidence of introduced insects.（Q30）',1,340354),(8998,183,'嗯，太棒了！ 谢谢你的见解，格兰特。 我希望你能启发我们这里的一些学生进行一些类似的实验。',361438,'Well, that''s fascinating! Thank you, Grant, for those insights. I hope that you might inspire some of our students here to conduct some similar experiments.',1,352177),(8999,184,'我最近在研究英国人如何看待那些首先被叫来医疗的医生，并将他们与其他国家的情况做对比。',86680,'I''ve been doing some research into what people in Britain think of doctors, the ones who work in general practice - the first call for medical care - and comparing this with the situation in a couple of other countries.',1,72144),(9000,184,'我想谈谈我决定做这件事的理由。',91480,'I want to talk about the rationale behind what I decided to do.',1,86683),(9001,184,'现在我不得不在三个不同的国家建立我的研究计划，所以我在海外部门联系了我所在领域的研究生，通过电子邮件与他们联系，在他们结束时为我安排事情。',106000,'Now I had to set up my programme of research in three different countries so I approached postgraduates in my field in overseas departments,（Q31） contacting them by email, to organise things for me at their end.',1,91485),(9002,184,'我以为我在寻求帮助时会遇到麻烦，但实际上每个人都非常愿意，有时他们的导师也会参与进来。',116000,'I thought I would have trouble recruiting help but in fact everyone was very willing and sometimes their tutors got involved too.',1,106000),(9003,184,'我必须向我的助手明确说明我希望他们使用什么样的样本总体。',123220,'I had to give my helpers clear instructions about what kind of sample population I wanted them to use.',1,116000),(9004,184,'我决定将 18 岁以下的人排除在外，因为他们中的大多数是学生或正在寻找第一份工作，而且我决定在这个阶段只关注有工作的男性，并为没有工作的人设置一些东西工作和就业妇女后来作为单独的调查。',145820,'I decided that people under 18 should be excluded because most of them are students or looking for their first job, and also I decided at this stage just to focus on men  who were in employment, and set up something for people who didn''t have jobs and for employed women later on as a separate investigation.（Q32）',1,123228),(9005,184,'我特别想做一个问卷调查，和一个焦点小组的访谈。',152000,'I specifically wanted to do a questionnaire, and interviews with a focus group.',1,145821),(9006,184,'使用问卷，而不是将其限制在一个特定的点上，我想包括尽可能多的多样性。',160630,'With the questionnaire, rather than limiting it to one specific point, I wanted to include as much variety as possible.（Q33）',1,152000),(9007,184,'我知道问卷调查是一种非常可控的做事方式，但我认为我可以稍后进行录音采访以抵消这种影响。',171020,'I know questionnaires are a very controlled way to do things but I thought I could do taped interviews later on to counteract the effects of this.',1,160631),(9008,184,'通过把对象限定在我可以轻易接触的范围内，这样焦点小组在以后也能派上用场，因为参与者往往更愿意投入到实验中。',182000,'And the focus group may also prove useful in future, by targeting subjects I can easily return to, as the participants tend to be more involved.',1,171027),(9009,184,'所以我现在只是在整理结果。',185510,'So I''m just collating the results now.',1,182000),(9010,184,'目前看来，在英国，尽管报纸不断报道人们对医疗服务不满意，但实际上他们担心的主要是在医院进行的第三级医疗服务。',202000,'At the moment it looks as if, in the UK, despite the fact that newspapers continually report that people are unhappy with medical care, in fact it is mainly the third level of care, which takes place in hospitals, that they are worried about.（Q34）',1,185510),(9011,184,'各级政府都提出了改革建议，尽管不能保证其成功，但长期住院治疗实际上可能不像媒体让我们相信的那样成为问题。',215680,'Government reforms have been proposed at all levels and although their success is not guaranteed, long-term hospital care is in fact probably less of an issue than the media would have us believe.',1,202000),(9012,184,'但是，我仍然有相当多的数据可供查看。',220000,'However, I''ve still got quite a bit of data to look at.',1,215686),(9013,184,'当然，我需要做比我预期的更深远的研究，以确定人们是否希望在社区中投入更多的医务人员，或者他们是否希望将护理恢复到更少但更大的关键医疗单位。',237460,'Certainly I will need to do more far-reaching research than I had anticipated in order to  establish if people want extra medical staff invested in the community, or if they want care to revert to fewer, but larger, key medical units.（Q35）',1,220000),(9014,184,'该解决方案很可能是地方政府负责人可以轻松实施的解决方案，当然还有中央政府的支持。',248000,'The solution may well be something that can be easily implemented by those responsible in local government, with central government support of course.',1,237464),(9015,184,'不过，这第一阶段已被证明非常有价值。',252000,'This first stage has proved very valuable though.',1,248000),(9016,184,'我对大多数受试者参与该项目的意愿感到惊讶——我曾预料到有些人不愿意诚实地回答问题。',261670,'I was surprised by how willing most of the subjects were to get involved in the project - I had expected some unwillingness to answer questions honestly.',1,252000),(9017,184,'但我很吃惊，我很担心我认为我设置得很好的东西在我自己部门的每个人看来并不一定是这样。',277330,'But i was taken aback and rather concerned that something I thought I''d set up very well didn''t necessarily seem that way to everyone in my own department.（Q36）',1,261670),(9018,184,'我想您可能也对我在收集数据时遇到的一些问题感兴趣。',284370,'I thought you might also be interested in some of the problems I encountered in collecting my data.',1,277330),(9019,184,'有一些奇怪的情况让我很震惊——我在城里购物时接触过的一个人，决定在第二轮比赛时退出。',295780,'There were odd cases that threw me - one of the subjects who I had approached while he was out shopping in town, decided to pull out when it came to the second round.（Q37）',1,284378),(9020,184,'很遗憾，因为这是我想更密切地采访的人。',302000,'It was a shame as it was someone who I would like to have interviewed more closely.',1,295780),(9021,184,'我采访的一位一年级学生想要确保自己的名字不会追踪到。',310000,