the charity.',1,93651),(9775,202,'这让我想到了最重要的部分。',105820,'Which brings me to the most important part.',1,102663),(9776,202,'这次徒步旅行是专门组织的，以帮助塞米拉地区的教育。',110810,'This trek is being specifically organized to help education in the Semira region.',1,105827),(9777,202,'去年我们帮助培训了残疾人教师，今年我们专注于学生。',117420,'Last year we helped train teachers for the disabled, and this year we''re focusing on the pupils.',1,110813),(9778,202,'每个步行者的赞助资金将用于帮助其中一所山区学校的个别特殊需要学生。',125000,'Each of the walkers'' sponsorship money will go to help an individual special needs pupil in one of the mountain schools.（Q13）',1,117428),(9779,202,'在演讲的第二部分，我将为您提供更多细节，但回到基本信息。',132330,'In the second part of the talk I''ll be giving you a lot more details, but back to the basic information.',1,125001),(9780,202,'年龄限制。',133480,'Age limits.',1,132333),(9781,202,'这是我们第二次举办这种假期，嗯，第一次我们甚至有一个八十岁的老人，但我们发现这次设立限制是明智的。',145000,'This is the second time we have run this kind of holiday and um, on the first we even had an eighty-year old, but we found it was wise to establish limits this time.',1,133484),(9782,202,'您必须至少年满 18 岁，现在的上限是 70 岁，但如果您超过 60 岁，则需要从医生那里获得健康证明。',155000,'You have to be at least eighteen and the top limit is now seventy, though you need to obtain a health certificate from your doctor if you are over sixty years old.',1,145001),(9783,202,'现在，塞米拉山脉是世界上最高的山脉之一，但你不要太害怕，我们主要只是在山脚下徒步旅行，虽然在山脚下也会有壮观的景色。',167430,'Now, the Semira Mountains are among the highest in the world but you mustn''t be too daunted, we will mainly be trekking in the foothills only, although there will be spectacular views even in the foothills.',1,155001),(9784,202,'但是，如果你现在身体不好，而且你有兴趣和我们一起去的话，你需要非常健康。',173950,'However, you will need to be extremely fit if you aren''t now and you''re interested in coming with us.（Q14）',1,167432),(9785,202,'你有足够的时间来锻炼身体。',177110,'You have plenty of time to get into shape.',1,173952),(9786,202,'您将睡在帐篷里，因此您必须随身携带相当多的设备，但您会得到当地助理的帮助。',184690,'You will be sleeping in tents so you must have quite a bit of equipment with you but you will be helped by local assistants.',1,177116),(9787,202,'您的床上用品等将由他们携带。',187750,'Your bedding and so forth will be carried by them.',1,184691),(9788,202,'我们要求您只带一个小背包步行，以满足当天的需要。',193030,'We ask that you only walk with a small rucksack with needs for the day.(Q15)',1,187759),(9789,202,'关于你将途经的景色真是美不胜收，说之不尽。',197760,'I don''t think I''ve really said enough about the marvellous area you''ll be walking in.',1,193032),(9790,202,'让我们看看您将看到的一些景点。',201020,'Let''s havea look at some of the sights you''ll be seeing.',1,197763),(9791,202,'除了这些壮观的白雪覆盖的山峰和山谷之外，还有许多历史悠久的村庄。',207350,'Apart from these spectacular snow-covered peaks and valleys, there are marvellous historic villages.',1,201023),(9792,202,'几个世纪以来，该地区一直以制作漂亮的地毯而闻名，尽管最近出现了编织毯子和木雕的趋势。',216460,'The area has been famous for centuries for making beautiful carpets(Q16), although recently there has been a trend to move into weaving blankets and wood carving.',1,207351),(9793,202,'人们非常友好和热情。',219330,'The people are extremely friendly and welcoming.',1,216461),(9794,202,'我们刻意保持聚会的规模较小，以尽量减少对人和景观的干扰。',262760,'We deliberately keep the parties small in size to minimize disruption to people and landscape.',1,219337),(9795,202,'我希望仍然有一些人感兴趣。',265560,'I hope that there are still some people interested.',1,262761),(9796,202,'我将在最后分发传单，您可以在其中找到更多信息，但现在我将概述行程，假期的主要亮点。',275530,'I will be distributing leaflets at the end where you can find out more information, but just for the moment I''ll outline the itinerary,\nthe main high points of the holiday.',1,265564),(9797,202,'显然，您将在第一天飞往首都基什巴。',280710,'Obviously, you''ll start by flying out to Kishba, the capital city, on Day One.',1,275535),(9798,202,'经过几天的适应后，您将在第三天开始徒步旅行，穿过巨大的卡蒂巴森林，这将花费一整天的时间。',290000,'After a couple of days to acclimatize yourself, you''ll start the trek on Day Three walking through the enormous Katiba Forest(Q17) which will take the whole of the day.',1,280713),(9799,202,'第四天带我们去更高的地方，穿过山麓，经过许多村庄，参观了 Schan 的一所残疾人学校。',298250,'Day Four takes us higher up, going through the foothills past a number of villages and\nvisiting a school for the disabled in Schan.',1,290001),(9800,202,'然后你有一个休息日，那是第五天，然后去壮观的库尔尼神庙，那里有十二世纪的雕刻，坐落在​​湖边的一个小森林里，那是第六天，许多人的亮点。',312540,'Then you have a rest day, that''s Day Five, before going to the spectacular Kumi Temple with twelfth-century carvings, set in a small forest by a lake and that''s Day Six, the highlight for many.(Q18)',1,298259),(9801,202,'我们在第七天附近呆在那里，因为那是最艰难的一天，穿过非常多山的国家，但最终在在帕特瀑布游泳。',322210,'We stay near there for Day Seven because\nthen comes the hardest day, walking through very mountainous country, but culminating in a\nswim in the Parteh Falls.',1,312546),(9802,202,'这是该地区最高的瀑布。',325000,'This is the highest waterfall in the region.(Q19)',1,322211),(9803,202,'第九天要容易得多，一天的一部分时间在一个村庄度过，在那里他们制作了一些华丽的红色毯子。',331700,'Day Nine is much easier, with part of the day spent in a village(Q20) where they make some of the gorgeous red blankets.',1,325000),(9804,202,'然后返回 Kishba 和回家的旅程。',335440,'Then back down to Kishba and the journey home.',1,331704),(9805,202,'所以你可以看到这是一个非常紧凑的时间表。',341100,'So you can see it''s a pretty packed timetable.',1,335443),(9806,203,'感谢大家今天来听听机器人漂浮项目如何帮助海洋研究。',65000,'Thanks to all of you for coming along today to hear about how the robotic float project is helping with ocean research.',1,57533),(9807,203,'好吧，首先我们来看看机器人漂浮物的作用及其用途。',69380,'Well, first of all we''ll look at what a robotic float does and its use.',1,65001),(9808,203,'因此，让我们从设备本身开始。',72190,'So let''s start with the device itself.(Q21)',1,69389),(9809,203,'它看起来有点像雪茄，长约一米半。',76390,'It looks a bit like a cigar and it''s about one and a half metres long.',1,72191),(9810,203,'更重要的是，它充满了旨在收集数据的设备。',80760,'More importantly it''s full of equipment that''s designed to collect data.',1,76395),(9811,203,'因此，它可以帮助我们建立一个不同因素的档案，这些因素在世界的海洋中共同发挥作用。',87180,'So, it can help us in building up a profile of different factors which work together within the world''s oceans.',1,80761),(9812,203,'听起来像是一个大项目——一个国家承担起来是不是太大了？',91920,'Sounds like a big project - isn''t it too big for one country to undertake?',1,87186),(9813,203,'确实如此，但这个项目是国际合作的一个很好的例子。',97740,'That''s quite true but this project is a really good example of international co-operation.',1,91928),(9814,203,'在过去五年中，来自 13 个国家的科学家参与了该项目，并在他们的海洋控制领域发射了漂浮物。',107040,'Over the last five years scientists from thirteen countries have been taking part in the project and launching floats in their area of ocean control.(Q22)',1,97748),(9815,203,'明年，当印度尼西亚加入该项目时，这个数字将上升到 14 个。',111790,'And next year this number will rise to fourteen when Indonesia joins the project.',1,107044),(9816,203,'这很让人佩服。',113080,'That''s impressive.',1,111795),(9817,203,'接下来我们来看浮舟的工作原理。',116290,'But let''s move onto how floats work.',1,113088),(9818,203,'操作的循环周期是这样的。',119320,'The operational cycle goes like this.',1,116296),(9819,203,'每个浮子在设定点从船上落入海中，并由卫星激活。',125370,'Each of the floats is dropped in the ocean from a boat at a set point and activated from a satellite.(Q23)',1,119325),(9820,203,'然后浮子立即下沉约 2,000 米……那是在水中整整两公里。',132320,'Then the float immediately sinks about 2,000 metres ... that''s two whole kilometres down in the water.',1,125375),(9821,203,'它在这个深度停留大约 10 天，并由在这个水平的海洋中运行的洋流携带。',139600,'It stays at this depth for about 10 days and is carried around by the currents which operate in the ocean at this level.',1,132327),(9822,203,'在此期间，它可以覆盖相当远的距离，但平均距离为 50 公里。',146110,'During this time it''s possible for it to cover quite large distances but the average is fifty kilometres.(Q24)',1,139602),(9823,203,'那么它实际上在记录什么？',148800,'So what is it actually recording?',1,146111),(9824,203,'好吧，在这个阶段什么都没有，但是当它上升到表面时，它会收集各种数据，最重要的是盐度的变化，即盐度和温度的变化，有点像水下气象气球。',164160,'Well at this stage nothing, but as it rises to the surface it collects all sorts of data, most importantly variations in salinity, that''s salt levels, and the changes in temperature, a bit like underwater weather balloons.(Q25)',1,148805),(9825,203,'然后，当它返回地面时，它收集的所有数据都会被传送到卫星上。',170000,'Then when it gets back to the surface all the data it''s collected is beamed up to the satellite.',1,164161),(9826,203,'在水面上大约五个小时后，浮子会自动下沉，重新开始整个过程。',176980,'After about five hours on the surface the float automatically sinks, beginning the whole process again.',1,170001),(9827,203,'数据会发生什么？',179060,'What happens to the data?',1,176986),(9828,203,'好吧，信息直接传输到陆上气象站，就像我们在霍巴特的气象站一样。并且在四个小时内，调查结果可以在计算机上，并且可以绘制和分析。',230000,'Well the information is transferred direct to onshore meteorological stations ... like our one in Hobart. .. and within four hours the findings can be on computers and they can be mapped and analysed.',1,179061),(9829,203,'您说您正在构建世界海洋系统的模型，但它们将如何使用，更重要的是，何时使用？',237540,'You say you''re building models of the world''s ocean systems but how''re they going to be used, and more importantly, when?',1,230001),(9830,203,'一些数据已经帮助完成了项目。例如，我们对厄尔尼诺事件根本原因的理解正在通过浮动数据得到证实。我们使用浮动数据的另一种方式是帮助我们了解气候变化的机制，例如全球变暖和臭氧消耗。',258060,'Some of the data has already helped in completing projects. For example, our understanding of the underlying causes of El Nino(Q26) events is being confirmed by float data. Another way we''re using float data is to help us to understand the mechanics of climate change, like global warming and ozone depletion.',1,237546),(9831,203,'这是正在进行的变异性研究的一部分，但结果还有很长的路要走。',263030,'That''s part of an ongoing variability study but the results are still a long way off.(Q27)',1,258067),(9832,203,'但是，我们的海洋天气预报并非如此。',267720,'However, this is not the case with our ocean weather forecasting.',1,263034),(9833,203,'因为我们从漂浮物上知道海洋某些地区的主要天气状况，所以我们可以就搜索和救援任务向海军提供建议。',276390,'Because we know from the floats what the prevailing weather conditions will be in certain parts of the ocean, we can advise the navy on search and rescue missions.',1,267722),(9834,203,'现在正在发生这种情况，许多游艇爱好者的生命都归功于这个项目的成功。',281890,'That''s happening right now and many yachtsmen owe their lives to the success of this project.(Q28)',1,276398),(9835,203,'此外，浮动数据可以帮助我们了解海洋过程的生物学意义。',287630,'In addition, the float data can 