p that used to be in the foyer, which sold books and CDs, is the one part of the redevelopment which isn''t yet complete.',1,75965),(10073,210,'计划是在剧院附近为寻找新的场地，我们很难找到合适的地方。',90450,'The plan is to find new premises for it near the theatre, and we''ve had difficulty finding somewhere suitable.',1,84012),(10074,210,'我们希望在未来几个月内重新开店。',93170,'We hope to reopen the shop in the next few months.（Q12）',1,90454),(10075,210,'观众会发现礼堂有什么不同吗？',97100,'Will audiences find any difference in the auditorium?',1,93174),(10076,210,'会的，我们增加了前后排间的腿部空间。',100800,'Yes, we''ve increased the leg-room between the rows.',1,97108),(10077,210,'这意味着现在座位减少了，但我们相信观众会更开心。',105960,'This means that there are now fewer seats（Q13） but we''re sure audiences will be much happier.\n',1,100809),(10078,210,'而且我们已经安装了空调，所以礼堂不会变得那么闷热和不透气。',110000,'And we''ve installed air conditioning, so it won''t get so hot and stuffy.',1,105962),(10079,210,'我们已经有一些适合轮椅使用者的座位，现在有两倍多的座位，我们希望能满足观众的需求。',117180,'We already had a few seats which were suitable for wheelchair users, and now there are twice as many（Q14）, which we hope will meet demand.',1,110001),(10080,210,'其他有利于观众的就是一个新的电梯。',120880,'Something else that will benefit audiences is the new lifts.',1,117181),(10081,210,'我们曾经拥有的两个电梯非常小而且很慢。',123800,'The two we used to have were very small and slow.',1,120882),(10082,210,'原来的现在已经拆了，我们有了更高效的。',127000,'They''ve now gone, and we''ve got much more efficient ones.（Q15）',1,123801),(10083,210,'对于表演者有什么改进吗？',129140,'Anything for the performers?',1,127003),(10084,210,'是的，我们在后台做了许多改进。',132480,'Yes, we''ve made a number of improvements backstage.',1,129141),(10085,210,'我们以前的狭窄而漆黑的更衣室被改造成两个通风的大房间，所以现在舒服多了。',140160,'The small, dark dressing rooms we used to have have been converted into two large airy rooms（Q16）, so they''re much more comfortable now.',1,132484),(10086,210,'并且安装了最先进的电子音响和照明系统。',176800,'And the stateof-the-art electronic sound and lighting systems have been installed.',1,140169),(10087,210,'好的，那么当剧院重新开放时，观众可以看到的第一部戏是什么？',183280,'OK, so what''s the first play that audiences can see when the theatre reopens?',1,176809),(10088,210,'我们有一个非常令人兴奋的彼得沙弗的皇家狩猎太阳，目前正在全国巡回演出。',188830,'We''ve got a very exciting production of Peter Shaffer''s Royal Hunt of the Sun, which is currently touring the country.',1,183286),(10089,210,'从 10 月 13 日开始，一直持续到 19 日。',193030,'That starts on October the 13th and runs till the 19th.（Q17）',1,188838),(10090,210,'我们正在对幕布升起的时间进行一些调试。',196240,'We''re experimenting a bit with the time the curtain goes up.',1,193037),(10091,210,'我们以前所有的演出都是在 7.30 开始，但这让人们很难乘坐公共交通工具回家，所以我们从 7 点开始，因为在 9.45 结束时，还有公共汽车在运行。',209620,'We used to start all our performances at 7.30, but that made it difficult for people to go home by public transport, so instead we''re beginning at 7（Q18）, because at 9.45, when it finishes, there are still buses running.',1,196241),(10092,210,'门票很畅销。',211900,'Tickets are already selling fast.',1,209622),(10093,210,'周五和周六的演出几乎立即售罄，事实上，现在只有周一和周四的门票。',218380,'The Friday and Saturday performances sold out almost immediately and, in fact, now there are only tickets for Monday and Thursday.（Q19）',1,211906),(10094,210,'门票多少钱？',220000,'How much are they?',1,218383),(10095,210,'我们采用了更简单的价格结构。过去的票价从6英镑到30英镑不等，但现在都是18英镑。可以从售票处、亲自、通过电话、传真或邮寄、或在线购买。',235000,'We''ve introduced a simpler price structure. Ticket prices used to range from £6 to £30 but now they''re all £ 18（Q20）. They''re available from the box office, in person, by phone, fax or post, or online.',1,220001),(10096,210,'好的，琳恩，现在如果你想提供剧院的联系方式...',240000,'OK, Lynne, now if you''d like to give the contact details for the theatre ...',1,235001),(10097,211,'你好，需要我帮忙吗？',46440,'Hello, can I help you?',1,44936),(10098,211,'我被告知要来这里，因为我想和某人谈谈参加管理课程的事情。',51470,'I was told to come here, because I''d like to talk to someone about taking a management course.',1,46448),(10099,211,'对。我是导师之一，所以我应该能够帮助你。',55470,'Right. I''m one of the tutors, so I should be able to help you.',1,51474),(10100,211,'哦，很好。我叫布赖恩·阿德利。我决定报读兼职管理课程。',