t OK?',1,347345),(11012,233,'没关系。',349590,'That''s fine.',1,348259),(11013,233,'它是 0-7-9-8-2-5-7-6-4-3。',355680,'It''s 0-7-9-8-2-5-7-6-4-3.',1,349595),(11014,233,'好的。关于你现在拥有的汽车，它是什么牌子的？',360650,'Fine. And about the car you have now, what make is it?',1,355685),(11015,233,'这是一个孔蒂。',362100,'It''s a Conti.',1,360656),(11016,233,'你知道年份或型号吗？',364390,'Do you know the year or the model name?',1,362104),(11017,233,'我想是 1996 年，它被称为狮子——就像动物一样。',370080,'I think it''s 1996, and it''s called a Lion（Q9） - like the animal.',1,364396),(11018,233,'然后一定是 1994 年，因为在那之后他们推出了 Fox。',375020,'Then it must be 1994, because they brought out the Fox after that.',1,370084),(11019,233,'哦，对，是的。',376560,'Oh right, yes.',1,375025),(11020,233,'里程？大致？',378380,'Mileage? Roughly?',1,376563),(11021,233,'我不知道。我知道不到七万。',382910,'I''m not sure. I know it''s less than seventy thousand.',1,378383),(11022,233,'好的。它是什么颜色？',386110,'OK. What colour is it?',1,382918),(11023,233,'它是灰色的，金属灰色。',389250,'It''s grey, metallic grey.',1,386116),(11024,233,'对，还有最后一件事——你会说它处于什么样的状态？',393440,'Right, and one last thing - what sort of condition would you say it''s in?',1,389254),(11025,233,'我可能会将其描述为合理的。你需要看看吗？它停在外面。',398570,'I''d probably describe it as reasonable（Q10）. Do you need to see it? It''s parked outside.',1,393448),(11026,233,'暂时不用，不了。也许你可以在下周的某一天打电话来...',402334,'Not at the moment, no. Perhaps you could call in one day next week...',1,398576),(11027,234,'正如我之前所说，我认为雷克斯福德将物理和地理优势完美地结合在一起 - 以及拥有乡村环境并且仍然靠近伦敦市中心，你肯定会感兴趣的是雷克斯福德离伦敦机场只有 35分钟。',68100,'As I said earlier, there is I think at Rexford an excellent combination of physical and geographical advantages - as well as having a rural setting and still being close to central London, something that will certainly be of interest to you is that Rexford is just 35 minutes from London Airport.（Q11）',1,47931),(11028,234,'在 Rexford，我们拥有强大的研究能力。在去年的研究评估中，我们在 101 所大学中排名第 7，该评估由政府机构进行，并且在您的特定学科、工程和科学方面表现特别出色。',87280,'At Rexford we have a strong research capability. We came 7th out of 101 universities in last year''s research assessment, carried out by a government body and did particularly well in your particular subjects, engineering and science.',1,68101),(11029,234,'实际上，我们在工程、地理和计算机科学方面获得了 5 分的最高研究成绩。',95050,'Actually we got a top research grade of five for engineering, geography and computer sciences.',1,87282),(11030,234,'还有一点——我从与你们单独交谈中了解到，你们中的一些人可能会在课程结束后寻求一些行业经验——是我们所有的科学和工程研究部门都与该领域的行业有着异常密切的关系。',114510,'One further point - and I know from talking to you individually that a number of you may be looking for some experience in industry after the course - is that all our science and engineering research departments have unusually close relationships with industry in the area.（Q12）',1,95051),(11031,234,'无论如何，我的销售谈话已经足够了......我会喝一口刚到的咖啡，谢谢，然后我会谈谈你申请时实际发生的事情。',125970,'Anyway that''s enough sales talk from me ... I''ll just take a sip of this coffee that''s just arrived, thank you, and then I''ll say something about what actually happens when you apply.',1,114519),(11032,234,'对……现在如果你决定提出申请，你要做的就是直接把它寄给我部门的我。',137040,'Right ... Now if you do decide to make an application, what you do is send it directly to me in my department.',1,125977),(11033,234,'然后，我将立即发送确认信息并开始申请流程。',142420,'I will then immediately send confirmation and the application process begins.',1,137045),(11034,234,'呃……我现在想说的是，如果这个过程不能很快奏效，你也不用担心——我的意思是偶尔会有邮政问题，但大多数情况下，拖延是由于——容我们说，您作为介绍人的人，要花时间回复。',161780,'Er ... I''d like to say at this point that you shouldn''t worry if this process doesn''t work all that quickly - I mean occasionally there are postal problems, but most often the hold-up is caused by references（Q13）- the people you give as referees, shall we say, take their time to reply.',1,142426),(11035,234,'无论如何，这个过程需要三到四个月是绝对正常的。',166380,'Anyway, it''s absolutely normal for this process to take three to four months.',1,161788),(11036,234,'在此期间，我所做的就是与您保持联系，并向您保证事情正在进展。',172870,'What I do in this period is keep in touch with you and reassure you that things are moving along.',1,166384),(11037,234,'我们设计的一种方法可以帮助您决定申请以及稍后何时被录取......希望......如果可能的话，让您与来自您自己国家的学生联系，他是目前和我们一起学习。',188240,'One of the ways we''ve devised to help you decide about applying as well as later when you''ve been accepted ... hopefully ... is to put you in contact with, if possible, a student from your own country（Q14） who is at present studying with us.',1,172874),(11038,234,'你能做的就是给他们打电话——我们当然会在你们之间联络——并与他们讨论你的担忧。',195720,'What you can do is phone them up - we will, of course, liaise between you - and discuss your concerns with them.',1,188242),(11039,234,'这样，您就可以客观地了解如果您来到 Rexford 生活和学习，您可以期待什么——不仅是学术氛围，还有重要的细节，比如休闲设施是什么样的，以及英国的天气和食物是否真的像每个人都说那样糟糕！',212920,'That way you can get an objective opinion of what you can expect if you come to live and study at Rexford - not only the academic atmosphere but important details like what the leisure facilities are like and whether（Q15） the English weather and food are really as awful as everybody says!',1,195720),(11040,234,'如果您决定可以面对它，该联系人还可以在您离开之前为您提供帮助，并提供有关打包什么之类的提示。',223440,'If you decide you can face it, the contact can also help you just before you leave, with tips on what to pack and that sort of thing.',1,212923),(11041,234,'目前我想我们有两个二年级学生和一个来自这个国家的研究生。',265410,'At the moment I think we''ve got two second-year students and one postgraduate from this country .',1,223449),(11042,234,'现在继续讨论您之前表达的其他担忧。在英国大学——我相信你知道——你将处于一个独立学习是常态的环境中，大多数学生需要一段时间来适应，而此时你将与正常的环境和，在大多数情况下，你的家人分开。',287520,'Now to move on to the other concerns you expressed earlier. At a UK university - as I''m sure you know - you will be in an environment where independent learning is the norm（Q16）, which takes most students a while to adjust to, and at a time when you will be separated from your normal surroundings and, in most cases, your family.',1,265418),(11043,234,'这可能是一个艰难的时期。但请记住，我们学生中有 25% 是像你们一样的国际学生，大学和城市中有几个组织的主要目的是提供帮助并确保您在我们这里度过愉快和有用的时光。',308190,'This can be a difficult time. But remember that something like 25% of our student body are international students like yourselves, and that there are several organisations in the university and city whose main purpose is to offer help and ensure that your time with us is enjoyable and useful.',1,287526),(11044,234,'你们中的一两个人早些时候谈到了住宿问题。',312380,'One or two of you touched on the subject of accommodation earlier.',1,308198),(11045,234,'所以我只补充几点：学校的政策是优先分配三类住宿名额，分别是访问生、交换生和新的研究生。',328120,'So I''ll just add a few points: it is the University''s policy to give priority in the allocation of residence places to three categories, and those are: visiting students, exchange students and new postgraduate students.（Q17）',1,312385),(11046,234,'然而，供不应求，所以仍然需要尽早为校园住宿报上名字，特别是如果您的家人陪伴您。',338330,'However, demand exceeds supply, so there is still a need to put your name down early for campus accommodation, particularly if your family is accompanying you.',1,328120),(11047,234,'这意味着您越早决定是否要与我们一起学习……因此推动程序进行，对每个人都越好。是的？',348900,'This means that the earlier you decide whether you want to study with us ... and so get the procedure moving, the better it will be for everybody. Yes?',1,338336),(11048,234,'如果您更愿意住在大学以外的地方怎么办？',352960,'What if you would prefer to live outside the university?',1,348900),(11049,234,'如果你打算住在校外，你必须更早地解决问题。',357680,'If you''re planning to live off-campus, you''ve got to sort things out even earlier.（Q18）',1,352968),(11050,234,'与所有供不应求的东西一样，好的住宿在学期开始前几个月就会被抢购一空——换句话说，如果你从 10 月开始，你需要在 6 月或最晚的 7 月考虑它。',372020,'As with everything in short supply, the good accommodation gets snapped up months before the beginning of term - in other words if you''re starting in October you need to be thinking about it in June or at the very latest July.',1,357681),(11051,234,'因此，您确实需要提前非常仔细地考虑您需要什么，您可以支付多少费用。',380420,'So you do need to think very carefully about what you need, how much you can afford to pay, well in advance.',1,372024),(11052,234,'你不能做的就是把它留到学期开始前几天。镇上的代理机构都不错——只是及时联系他们的问题。',391920,'What you can''t do is leave it until a few days before the start of term. The agencies in town are pretty good - it''s just a matter of contacting them in good time.',1,380425),(11053,234,'当然，我们有一个全职的住宿官员可以帮助所有的学生。',397240,'Of course, we have a full-time accommodation officer available to help all students.',1,391924),(11054,234,'当你被录取时，她会与你取得联系——她在镇上有很多联系人，并代表你与代理机构打交道。',405890,'She''ll get in touch with you when you''re accepted - she''s got plenty of contacts in the town and deal with the agencies on your behalf.（Q19）',1,397249),(11055,234,'你们中的一两个人早些时候问过我你的英语口语水平。',410420,'One or two of you asked me earlier about your level of spoken English .',1,405898),(11056,234,'显然，你们中的大多数人已经取得了很多成就——我希望我能说你们的语言一半。 话虽如此，但恐怕讲师会很少或根本不考虑听众中非母语人士的存在。',425000,'Obviously most of you have already achieved a lot - I wish I could speak your language half as well. Having said that though, I''m afraid the lecturers will make little or no allowance for the presence of non-native speakers in the audience.',1,410429),(11057,234,'因此，您可以做的任何事情来提高您的英语口语——甚至超出你们大多数人已经达到的相当高的水平——都将有助于让您在我们这里逗留更有趣。',437150,'So anything you can do to improve your spoken English - even beyond the pretty high levels most of you have already reached - will help make your stay with us that bit more fun for you.',1,425009),(11058,234,'在你到达之前进行一些额外的练习比......例如之后的私人课程，当你真的没有时间时，更值得。',445650,'Some extra practice before you arrive（Q20） is worth more than ... for example private lessons afterwards, when you won''t really have time.',1,437157),(11059,234,'哦......在我提出进一步问题之前的最后一件事：你......',452130,'Oh ... and one last thing before I invite further questions: it''s very important that you ...',1,445657),(11060,235,'哦，本——我刚想起来我从来没有为尼克填过那张表格——你填了吗？',47540,'Oh Ben - I just remembered I never filled in that form for Nick - did you do it?',1,40989),(11061,235,'课程反馈表？',48580,'The course feedback form?',1,47540),(11062,235,'是的。如果你愿意，我们可以一起做，我这里有我的。',53080,'Yes. If you want, we can do it together, I''ve got mine here.',1,48586),(11063,235,'那样可以么？',53840,'Is that OK?',1,53088),(11064,235,'是的。',54370,'Yeah.',1,53849),(11065,235,'好的，那我们来看看。我们需要做什么？',58720,'OK, let''s have a look then. What do we have to do?',1,54377),(11066,235,'我们先填上最上面，我们看看，课程，课程编号 ...',64660,'Let''s fill in the top first, let''s see, Course, Course code ...',1,58720),(11067,235,'呃，是商务沟通。',67790,'Er, it''s Communication in Business.',1,64662),(11068,235,'好的，沟通......在......商业，我知道，但代码是什么？',74890,'OK, Communication ... in ... Business, I do know that, but what''s the code?',1,67798),(11069,235,'CB 16 什么，CB 162，不是吗？',79860,'CB 16 something, CB 162, isn''t it?',1,74899),(11070,235,'嗯，就是这样，好的，日期，我们什么时候开始的？我记得，我的生日是 5 月 4 日，那是后一天，一定是 5 月 5 日。',90900,'Mmm, that''s it, OK and dates, when did we start? I remember, my birthday''s on May 4th and it was the day after, it must have been May 5th.（Q21）',1,79866),(11071,235,'天哪，似乎不是很久以前，是吗？',92930,'Gosh, doesn''t seem that long ago, does it?',1,90900),(11072,235,'不，我们在本周末结束，周五，所以是 7 月 15 日？',98800,'No, and we finish at the end of this week, on Friday, so that''s July（Q22） 15th?',1,92930),(11073,235,'呃十六号，星期一是十二号。 对，这很简单，现在让我们来看看——“请对课程的以下方面发表你的意见”。 好的，第一个是什么？ 哦，课程组织。 你怎么看？',114540,'Er 16th, Monday was the 12th. Right, that was the easy bit, now let''s have a look - \"Please give your comments on the following aspects of the course\". OK, what''s the first one? Oh, course organisation. What do you think?',1,98805),(11074,235,'呃，清楚吗？是的，不是吗？',117810,'Er, clear? It was, wasn''t it?',1,114544),(11075,235,'是的，我认为组织很清楚。好的，还有什么课程组织的吗？',123290,'Yes, I think the organisation was clear.（Q23） OK, anything else for course organisation?',1,117815),(11076,235,'好在他在一开始就给了我们课程大纲，在第一节课上，这很有用，所以我会把它记下来，好吗？',131860,'It was a good thing he gave us the course outline（Q24） at the beginning, in the first session, that was useful, so I''ll put that down, shall I?',1,123299),(11077,235,'现在，继续提出改进建议，一件不太好的事情，我认为我们一开始可以做更多的工作，我的意思是一开始看起来很容易。',143990,'Now, going on to suggestions for improvement, one thing that wasn''t so good, I think we could have done a bit more work at the beginning, I mean at the 