e key texts before the session, how are you supposed to do the reading?',1,255335),(11091,235,'而且电脑不够用。你必须等待很长时间才能得到一个。',265480,'And not enough computers. You have to wait ages to get one.',1,260807),(11092,235,'好的，测试和评估——嗯，我不知道，在我们收到书面作业之前很难说。',272350,'OK, testing and evaluation - well, I don''t know, it''s hard to say until we''ve got our written assignments back.',1,265487),(11093,235,'别说这个，我昨天才拿到我的，那是一场真正的斗争。',278090,'Don''t talk about it, I only got mine in yesterday, it was a real struggle.',1,272355),(11094,235,'我不想去想我会得到什么分数。',281590,'I hate to think what mark I''ll get.',1,278099),(11095,235,'是的，但至少我们已经完成了口头报告——我认为这很好，我很快就得到了反馈。',288080,'Yes, but at least we''ve done the oral presentation - I thought that was good, the way I got my feedback really quickly.',1,281599),(11096,235,'是的。我喜欢我们知道我们将被评估的方式，我们知道标准，所以我们知道我们必须考虑清晰度、组织等等。',299110,'Yes, it was. And I liked the way we knew what we''d be evaluated on, we knew the criteria, so we knew we had to think about clarity, organisation, and so on.',1,288085),(11097,235,'是的，但我对书面工作不太确定。',301170,'Yeah, but I''m not so sure about the written work.（Q29）',1,299110),(11098,235,'我认为的一件事是太多了，压力真的很大。',306230,'One thing I think is that there''s just too much, it''s really stressful.',1,301171),(11099,235,'是的，我同意，我不明白他们为什么不能让我们知道他们用于评分的标准。',312260,'Yes, I''d agree and I don''t see why they can''t let us know the criteria they use for marking.',1,306231),(11100,235,'书面作业？但他告诉我们。',314400,'The written assignments? But he told us.',1,312267),(11101,235,'不，期末考试的。他们在寻找什么——标准是什么？什么使通过或失败？',322220,'No, for the final exams. What are they looking for - what are the criteria? What makes a pass or a fail?',1,314404),(11102,235,'是的，我从没想过。这真的很有用。',325020,'Yeah, I never thought of that. It''d be really useful.',1,322226),(11103,235,'好的，还有其他意见吗？',328170,'OK, any other comments?',1,325020),(11104,235,'我认为学生的支持非常好。',331280,'I thought student support was excellent.（Q30）',1,328172),(11105,235,'我也是。好的，太好了。其他的建议？',337270,'Yeah, me too. OK, excellent. Other comments?',1,331287),(11106,235,'不，我想不出别的了。',339860,'No, I can''t think of anything else.',1,337271),(11107,235,'我也不。好的，这样就完成了。谢谢，本。',344310,'Nor me. OK, so that''s done. Thanks, Ben.',1,339867),(11108,235,'不，谢谢。',345910,'No, thank you.',1,344317),(11109,236,'嗯，我的团队一直在做一个关于如何在英国回收家庭垃圾的项目。',68620,'Well, my group has been doing a project on how household waste is recycled in Britain.',1,61982),(11110,236,'我们非常震惊地发现，在英国只有 9% 的人努力回收他们的家庭垃圾。',77700,'We were quite shocked to discover that only 9% of people here in the UK make an effort to recycle their household waste.',1,68623),(11111,236,'这个数字低于大多数其他欧洲国家，如果政府要实现其回收目标，未来几年需要大幅增加。',88720,'This is a lower figure than in most other European countries, and needs to increase dramatically in the next few years if the government is going to meet its recycling targets.',1,77707),(11112,236,'英国商定的目标意味着到 2008 年，我们必须将我们的二氧化碳排放量比 1990 年减少 12.5%。',100240,'The agreed targets for the UK mean that by 2008 we must reduce our carbon dioxide emissions by 12.5%（Q31） compared with 1990.',1,88720),(11113,236,'回收可以通过两种主要方式帮助实现这一目标：回收玻璃和纸张的生产比用原始材料生产它们使用的能源要少得多，而且回收还可以减少垃圾填埋场和焚烧厂的温室气体排放。',121180,'And recycling can help to achieve that goal, in two main ways: the production of recycled glass and paper uses much less energy than producing them from virgin materials, and also recycling reduces greenhouse gas emissions from landfill sites and incineration plants.（Q32）',1,100242),(11114,236,'作为我们项目的一部分，我们对街上的人们进行了一项调查，一次又一次出现的问题是人们认为回收废物并不容易。',135060,'As part of our project, we carried out a survey of people in the street, and the thing that came up over and over again is that people don''t think it''s easy enough to recycle their waste.',1,121182),(11115,236,'一个问题是没有足够的“垃圾收集点”，即公众应该收集垃圾的地方。',142580,'One problem is that there aren''t enough ''drop-off（Q33） sites'', that is, the places where the public are supposed to take their waste.',1,135063),(11116,236,'我们还发现，从住户那里收集的垃圾会被带到一个叫做“带库”的地方，进行分类和打包成负载。',152490,'We also discovered that waste that''s collected from householders is taken to places called ''bring banks'', for sorting and baling into loads.',1,142581),(11117,236,'这里的一个问题是把不应该放在回收容器里的东西都拿出来：人们把各种各样的东西放进瓶子里，比如塑料袋，甚至是坏掉的雨伞。',165560,'One problem here is taking out everything that shouldn''t have been placed in the recycling containers: people put all sorts of things into bottle banks, like plastic bags and even broken umbrellas.',1,152491),(11118,236,'所有这些都必须手动移除。',168530,'All this has to be removed by hand.',1,165565),(11119,236,'另一个困难是用于烹饪的钢化玻璃在其他玻璃所需的温度下不会完全熔化，因此也必须用手将其取出。',180070,'Another difficulty is that toughened glass used for cooking（Q34） doesn''t fully melt at the temperature required for other glass, and so that also has to be picked out by hand.',1,168536),(11120,236,'玻璃很容易回收，因为它可以一遍又一遍地重复使用而不会变弱。',186920,'Glass is easy to recycle because it can be reused over and over again without becoming weaker.',1,180079),(11121,236,'每年扔掉200万吨玻璃，即70亿瓶和罐；但其中只有 500,000 吨被收集和回收。',205130,'Two million tons of glass is thrown away each year, that is, seven billion bottles and jars; but only 500,000（Q35） tons of that is collected and recycled.',1,186928),(11122,236,'奇怪的是，收集的玻璃中有一半是绿色的，其中很多是进口的，因此回收的绿色玻璃比英国需要的多。',214940,'Oddly enough, half the glass that''s collected is green, and a lot of that is imported, so more green glass is recycled than the UK needs.',1,205132),(11123,236,'因此，正在开发再生玻璃，特别是绿色玻璃的新用途，例如在玻璃纤维制造和水过滤中。',226480,'As a result, new uses are being developed for recycled glass, particularly green glass, for example in fibreglass manufacture and water filtration.',1,214946),(11124,236,'一家名为 CLF Aggregates 的公司生产用于道路的产品，其中 30% 的材料是碎玻璃。',234820,'A company called CLF Aggregates makes a product for roads（Q36）, and 30% of the material is crushed glass.',1,226484),(11125,236,'在回收纸方面，英国以 40% 位居欧洲第二，仅次于德国惊人的 70%。',243850,'For recycling paper, Britain comes second in Europe with 40%, behind Germany''s amazing 70%.',1,234822),(11126,236,'开始回收时，出现了质量问题，因此在办公打印机中很难使用再生纸。',252670,'When recycling started, there were quality problems, so it was difficult to use recycled paper in office printers.',1,243853),(11127,236,'但是这些问题现在已经解决了，位于伦敦南部的 Martin''s 生产了一系列 100% 可回收的办公文具，成本与普通纸相同，质量也同样出色。',268190,'But these problems have now been solved, and Martin''s, based in South London, produces a range of office stationery which is 100% recycled, costs the same as normal paper and is of equally high quality.',1,252671),(11128,236,'但是，这种高质量是以过程中产生的废物为代价的。',274110,'But this high quality comes at a cost in terms of the waste produced during the process.',1,268197),(11129,236,'超过三分之一的废纸不能用于再生纸，留下了如何处理的问题。',281740,'Over a third of the waste paper that comes in can''t be used in the recycled paper, leaving the question of what to do with it.',1,274114),(11130,236,'一家名为 Papersave 的公司目前将其作为土壤改良剂出售给农民，但由于运输成本和气味的原因，这种做法很快就会被禁止，该公司正在研究替代用途的可能性。',297680,'One firm, Papersave, currently sells this to farmers as a soil conditioner（Q37）, though this practice will soon be banned because of transport costs and the smell, and the company is looking into the possibility of alternative uses.',1,281745),(11131,236,'塑料会引起问题，因为当今使用的塑料种类繁多，每种都必须以不同的方式处理。',306790,'Plastic causes problems, because there are so many different types of plastic in use today, and each one has to be dealt with differently.',1,297685),(11132,236,'Pacrite 回收各种各样的东西，从瓶子到汽车保险杠，它最成功的活动之一是回收塑料瓶来制造容器，这些容器在全国范围内用于收集废物。',320570,'Pacrite recycles all sorts of things, from bottles to car bumpers, and one of its most successful activities is recycling plastic bottles to make containers（Q38） which are used all over the country to collect waste.',1,306792),(11133,236,'Save-a-Cup 计划是由自动售货机和塑料行业制定的，旨在尽可能多地回收每年使用的 35 亿个聚苯乙烯杯。',333270,'The Save-a-Cup scheme was set up by the vending and plastics industries to recycle as many as possible of the three-and-a-half billion polystyrene cups used each year.',1,320577),(11134,236,'目前，有 5 亿个 polycups 被收集、加工并出售给其他企业，例如 Waterford，后者将这些杯子变成铅笔。',343850,'At the moment 500 million polycups are collected, pro