e worth spending some time in, and they''re open all day, from eight to six, so we can go there any time.',1,262443),(11490,245,'我也想去河边的市场，但是哦不，等等，那也只是在早上。',279540,'I''d like to go to the Markets near the river too, but oh no, wait, that''s only in the mornings, too.',1,271121),(11491,245,'除了今天和明天，我们可以在星期一看到其他地方，你知道的。',284030,'As well as today and tomorrow, we can see some other places on Monday, you know.',1,279544),(11492,245,'但我不认为市场会在那时开放：它们只在星期四开放，所以我们本周错过了它们。',290160,'But I don''t think the Markets will be open then(Q7): they only open on Thursdays, so we''ve missed them for this week.',1,284031),(11493,245,'也许我们今天应该去大教堂，因为明天是星期天，即使它每天都开放，但由于教堂服务，明天可能更难进入。',300040,'Maybe we should go to the Cathedral today because it''s Sunday tomorrow, and even though it''s open every day it might be more difficult to get in tomorrow because of the church services.',1,290167),(11494,245,'没错，但是美术馆周日根本不开门，所以我们今天必须去那里。',307140,'That''s true, but the Art Gallery isn''t open on Sundays at all, so we''ll have to go there today.',1,300047),(11495,245,'除了星期一，城堡每天都开放，所以我们可以在那里，当然花园只在晚上关闭。',313880,'The Castle''s open every day except Mondays, so we''re OK there, and the Gardens of course only close at night.',1,307141),(11496,245,'这些地方都是免费的还是必须付费才能进去？旅游指南是怎么说的？。',319540,'Are all these places free or do we have to pay to go in? What does the guidebook say?',1,313883),(11497,245,'我认为除了植物园之外，所有这些都需要收费。',323560,'I think there''s a charge for all of them except the Botanical Gardens(Q8).',1,319546),(11498,245,'哦，还有市场，当然你不需要付钱进去。',326420,'Oh, and the Markets, of course you don''t pay to go in.',1,323562),(11499,245,'好的，好吧，看来我们的计划是这样的：我们先去看你喜欢的画，伦勃朗，然后吃午饭，然后去城堡，然后是大教堂。',339620,'OK, well, it looks like our plan is this: we''ll go to see the painting you like first(Q9), the Rembrandt, then have lunch and go on to the Castle after that, and then the Cathedral.',1,326423),(11500,245,'好的，这里说大教堂的屋顶真的很漂亮。',344270,'OK, It says here that the roof of the Cathedral is really beautiful.',1,339623),(11501,245,'是这样吗？我在大教堂真正想做的就是爬塔。',349040,'Is that right?What I really want to do at the Cathedral is climb the tower(Q10).',1,344272),(11502,245,'景色应该很壮观。',351460,'The view is supposed to be spectacular.',1,349041),(11503,245,'好的，好吧，这对于今天来说已经绰绰有余了。',355360,'OK, well, that''ll be more than enough for today.',1,351462),(11504,245,'那么，明天，我们去植物园野餐吧。',359080,'Then, tomorrow, let''s go to the Botanical Gardens and have a picnic.',1,355364),(11505,245,'我想坐在河边看天鹅。',361670,'I want to sit by the river and watch the swans.',1,359081),(11506,245,'这座城市以它们而闻名。',363130,'This city''s famous for them.',1,361671),(11507,246,'因此，我们提供的咨询服务可以解决您在学习或大学以外的生活中出现的任何问题。',53010,'So the counselling services we offer deal with any problems arising from your studies, or in your life outside the university.',1,42832),(11508,246,'让我们进行学术咨询。',55580,'Let''s take academic counselling.',1,53015),(11509,246,'如果您对科目或如何将它们结合到您的学位中感到困惑，那么我们可以为您提供建议并讨论您的目标职业，以便您可以在上下文中看到这一切。',67780,'If you''re confused about subjects or how to combine them in your degree, then we can advise you and discuss the career you are aiming for, so that you can see it all in context.',1,55586),(11510,246,'如果你没有得到关于你在你的科目上的正确反馈，我们也可以追你的导师。',73950,'We can also chase up your tutor if you''re not getting proper feedback on how you are getting on in your subject(Q11).',1,67782),(11511,246,'除了学业问题的帮助外，您可能还需要个人咨询：如果您认为自己已经处于压力之下，那就等到下周开始上课吧。',85920,'Besides help with academic problems, you may also need personal counselling: if you think you''re already under stress, well, just wait till classes begin next week.',1,73956),(11512,246,'您将不得不开始适应您可能不熟悉的教学和学习方法，以及随着第一次作业的最后期限临近而越来越大的压力。',96800,'You''ll have to start adjusting to teaching and learning methods that may be unfamiliar to you, as well as the mounting pressure as the deadline for that first assignment(Q12) creeps up on you.',1,85923),(11513,246,'当然，你必须在没有你通常的社交网络的情况下应对所有这些 - 你知道，你通常可以依赖的社交联系人、家人和朋友来寻求帮助。',108810,'And of course, you have to cope with all this without your usual social network - you know, the social contacts, family and friends (Q13)you could normally rely on for help.',1,96808),(11514,246,'所有这些都会引起焦虑。',111310,'All of this causes anxiety.',1,108812),(11515,246,'出国留学可能会引发个人危机——你可能把很多你可能称之为“未完成的事业”的事情留在了自己的国家，或者你可能中断了个人关系，甚至有时为了出国而断绝了关系，因此学生经常感到孤独、不快乐、没有动力，无法专心学习。',137020,'Studying overseas can trigger a personal crisis - you may have left a lot of what you might call ''unfinished business'' back in your own country, or you may have interrupted personal relationships(Q14) or even sometimes have broken them off to come overseas, and so the student often feels lonely, unhappy, unmotivated and unable to concentrate on studying.',1,111314),(11516,246,'或者可能还有其他事情困扰着你。',140570,'Or there may be other things bothering you.',1,137029),(11517,246,'如果您愿意，我们的常驻牧师可以为您提供精神指导，或者我们可以让您与可以为您提供社交联系和友谊的社区团体联系。',187770,'Our resident chaplain can offer you spiritual guidance if that''s what you want, or we can put you in touch with community groups that can provide you with social contacts and friendship.',1,140577),(11518,246,'考试压力呢？它在某种程度上影响了几乎每个人，尤其是像你们这样的海外学生。',196540,'What about exam stress? It affects nearly everyone to some extent, but especially overseas students like yourselves.',1,187776),(11519,246,'可能会有巨大的家庭压力要求你成功，如果你因为一门学科太难而失败或退出一门学科，那么你的自尊心就会受到影响。',207970,'There may be a huge amount of family pressure on you to succeed, and if you fail a subject or drop out of a course(Q15) because it’s too difficult then your self-esteem can suffer.',1,196547),(11520,246,'但是，如果你不通过考试，这不是世界末日——我不得不重考人类学一年级，所以我当然可以给你一个同情的耳朵！',218600,'But it''s not the end of the world if you don''t pass an exam - I had to resit First Year Anthropology, so I can certainly offer you a sympathetic ear!',1,207973),(11521,246,'无论如何，考试失败会导致您通常的行为方式发生令人担忧的变化。',224100,'Anyway, exam failure can lead to worrying changes in the way you normally behave.',1,218602),(11522,246,'你也可能不吃东西，或者你可能有饮食问题，因为当地的食物不合你的胃口，让你心烦意乱，这会影响你的健康和学习。',235430,'You may also be off your food, or you may have dietary problems because the local food is not to your liking(Q16) and upsets you, and this can affect your health and studies.',1,224101),(11523,246,'Glenda Roberts 是我们在健康服务部门的营养师，我们可以为您介绍她。',241540,'Glenda Roberts is our dietician in the Health Service and we can put you on to her.',1,235435),(11524,246,'而且我们都有钱的问题，不是吗？但请记住，全日制学生可以获得高达 600 美元的低息贷款，用于购买书籍和类似的学习相关费用。',254880,'And we all have money problems, don''t we? But remember, full-time students can get a low-interest loan of up to six hundred dollars to buy books(Q17) and for similar study-related expenses.',1,241546),(11525,246,'没错，如果您买不起课程所需的设备（例如乐器），您可以获得双倍的金额。',264230,'That''s right, and you can get double that amount if you can’t afford an item of equipment you need for your course - a musical instrument, for example.',1,254881),(11526,246,'它并不止于此。',266000,'And it doesn''t stop there.',1,264235),(11527,246,'当您搬进公寓时，包括家具在内的启动费用可以通过福利服务部门的贷款来支付 - 详情请参阅 Jill Freeman。',278060,'When you move into a flat, starting-up expenses, including furniture(Q18) for it, can be covered by a loan through the Welfare Service - see Jill Freeman for details.',1,266001),(11528,246,'我们能帮助你吗？上个学年，尽管在裁员，我们为国际生提供了总计2600个小时的咨询服务，最后除了代表学生开启的12个恳求中的一个，其他的我们都完成了。',297450,'Can we help you? Well, last academic year, in spite of staff cuts, we counselled two hundred and forty(Q19) international students for a total of twenty-six hundred hours counselling, and, finally we won all but just one of the twelve appeals that we launched on behalf of students.',1,278066),(11529,246,'对于人手不足的服务来说还不错，你不觉得吗？这就是我要说的。',302880,'Not too bad for an understaffed service(Q20), don''t you think? That''s all from me.',1,297456),(11530,246,'谢谢你。',303970,'Thank you.',1,302888),(11531,247,'哦，你来了，很好。',42210,'Oh, there you are, good.',1,39709),(11532,247,'抱歉，我来晚了——排了很长的队。',45690,'Sorry I''m a bit late - there was a long queue.',1,42210),(11533,247,'那么，你想好怎么处理这个作业了吗？',49500,'So, have you worked out how to deal with this assignment then?',1,45696),(11534,247,'还没有，我们自己才来了几分钟。',52610,'Not yet, we''ve only been here a couple of minutes ourselves.',1,49501),(11535,247,'你能提醒我具体的任务是什么吗？',55400,'Can you just remind me what the task is exactly?',1,52612),(11536,247,'好吧，它有两个，不，三个部分：首先，我们必须写一篇关于收集数据的方法的文章。然后......',64800,'Well, there are two, no, three, parts to it: first, we''ve got to write an essay about ways of collecting data. Then ....',1,55401),(11537,247,'这篇论文的标题到底是什么？',67210,'What''s the title of the essay exactly?',1,64806),(11538,247,'我在这里找到了：“评估在社会科学研究中收集数据的两种主要方法”。',73910,'I''ve got it here: ‘Assess the two main methods of collecting data(Q21) in social science research’.',1,67217),(11539,247,'我们需要写多少？',76350,'And how much do we need to write?',1,73918),(11540,247,'一千五百字，这是作文。',79970,'Fifteen hundred(Q22) words.That''s for the essay.',1,76354),(11541,247,'然后，对于作业的第二部分，我们必须选择一种数据收集方法，并“进行小规模研究，适当使用选择的方法从至少五个受试者中收集数据”。',92380,'Then, for the second part of the assignment, we have to choose one method of data collection, and ''carry out a small-scale study, making appropriate use of the method chosen to gather data from at least five(Q23) subjects''.',1,79975),(11542,247,'然后我们要写一份研究报告？',94770,'And then we have to write a report on the study?',1,92389),(11543,247,'没错，三四千字。',97360,'That''s right, of three to four thousand(Q24) words.',1,94777),(11544,247,'您是否讨论过我们应该采用哪种形式的数据收集 - 问卷调查或访谈，不是吗？',104750,'Did you get as far as discussing which form of data collection we should go for - questionnaire or interview , isn''t it?',1,97368),(11545,247,'是的，我认为我们应该使用问卷调查。',107130,'Yeah, I think we should use a questionnaire.',1,104750),(11546,247,'我想，这会比组织面试花的时间少得多。',110560,'It''ll be so much less time-consuming than organising interviews, I reckon.',1,107136),(11547,247,'一旦我们就其措辞达成一致，我们只需将其发送出去并等待回复。',115770,'Once we''ve agreed on the wording of it, we only have to send it out and wait for the responses.',1,110567),(11548,247,'是的，我认为它可能会更快。',118740,'Yes, I think it probably would be quicker.',1,115772),(11549,247,'但他上周给我们的那篇文章对调查问卷数据的质量有什么看法？'