训练。',136920,'Right  not sure I''ve ever run that far so I''d better start doing a bit of training.',1,130734),(11998,257,'这是个好主意。但这不是一场比赛，这真的只是为了好玩，最好的办法是在最初的几次比赛中放轻松，然后看看你是否可以逐渐提高你的时间。',151190,'That''s a good idea. But it’s not a race, it''s really just for fun and the best thing would be to take it easy the first few times you do it and then see if you can gradually improve your time.',1,136928),(11999,257,'那么跑步是否有时间限制？我怎么知道我做得怎么样？',156730,'Is the run timed then? How do I know how well I''ve done?',1,151190),(12000,257,'当你越过终点线时，你会得到一个条形码，然后你把它交给一位跑步志愿者，他会扫描它。然后你回家后可以在网上查到你的时间。',168550,'When you cross the finish line you''ll be given a bar code and you take this to one of the run volunteers, who will scan it. Then you can get your time online when you go home.(Q4)',1,156739),(12001,257,'哦，我明白了。您收集所有结果。',172450,'Oh - I see. You collect all the results.',1,168552),(12002,257,'没错！',173740,'Exactly.',1,172450),(12003,257,'我明白了——太好了。那么我该如何注册呢？',179310,'I see - that''s great. So how do I register?',1,173740),(12004,257,'那么有几种方法。我可以通过电话获取您的详细信息，但如果您使用网站进行操作会容易得多。',188390,'Well there are several ways. I could take your details over the phone but it''s much easier if you do it using the website.(Q5)',1,179312),(12005,257,'好的 - 好。嗯，我想这可能就是我现在需要知道的全部了。哦，是的，注册要花什么钱吗？或者你每周都收钱吗？',201610,'OK - good. Um, I think that''s probably all I need to know for w. Oh yes - does it cost anything to register or do you collect money each week?',1,188394),(12006,257,'好吧，注册不需要任何费用，但我们会为跑步收费。事实上，我们刚刚将费用提高到 1.50 英镑。它曾经是一磅，但因为我们亏损了一点，我们不得不将它增加 50 便士。',218930,'Well it doesn''t cost anything to register but we do charge for the run. In fact we have just increased the charge to £1.50. It used to be a pound but because we were making a bit of a loss we have had to increase it by 50p.(Q6)',1,201616),(12007,257,'好，谢谢。我想我有足够的信息参加跑步。',258650,'OK thanks. I think I have enough information on taking part in the run.',1,218932),(12008,257,'嗯，你提到了志愿者。我有一个朋友有兴趣帮忙。你能给我一些细节，以便我把它们传给她吗？',269870,'Um - you mentioned volunteers. I have a friend who is interested in helping out. Can you give me some details so I can pass them on to her?',1,258656),(12009,257,'当然 - 好吧，您需要让您的朋友联系 Pete Maughan。他管理着所有的志愿者。',277380,'Sure - well you need to ask your friend to contact Pete Maughan. He manages all the volunteers.(Q7)',1,269872),(12010,257,'好吧——我没听懂他的姓——是早上吗——M-O-R-N？',286530,'OK - I didn''t quite catch his surname - was it Morn - M-O-R-N?',1,277384),(12011,257,'不——只是稍微复杂一点——它是 M-A-U-G-H-A-N。',295510,'No - just a bit more complicated - it''s M-A-U-G-H-A-N.',1,286530),(12012,257,'对 - 谢谢。你能给我他的电话号码吗？',300540,'Right - thanks. And could you give me his phone number?',1,295511),(12013,257,'是的 - 只是片刻。它在某个地方——让我找到它。啊，我有他的两个号码。我认为以 0-1-2-7-3 开头的那个是旧的，所以使用这个 0-1-4-4-4-7-3-2-9-0-0。',328010,'Yes - just a moment. It''s here somewhere - let me just find it. Ah I''ve two numbers for him. I think the one that begins 0-1-2-7-3 is an old one so use this one 0-1-4-4-4-7-3-2-9-0-0.(Q8)',1,300541),(12014,257,'好的，我明白了。你能告诉我一些关于志愿服务的事情吗？比如它涉及什么样的活动？',337890,'OK - got that. Can you tell me anything about the volunteering? Like what kind of activities it involves?',1,328016),(12015,257,'当然，我们需要志愿者来做一些基本的事情，比如设置课程。我们必须在所有跑步者到达之前做到这一点。',347420,'Sure - well we need volunteers for basic stuff like setting up the course. We have to do that before all the runners arrive.',1,337896),(12016,257,'好吧，这真的开始地非常早！',350670,'OK - so that''s a really early start!',1,347422),(12017,257,'是的，这是对的。但是，如果您的朋友希望晚一点到达，她也可以帮助指导跑步者，以免他们走错路。',361140,'Yes that''s right. But if your friend would prefer to arrive a bit later she can also help with guiding the runners so they don''t go the wrong way.(Q9)',1,350678),(12018,257,'我知道了。我相信你会报告一些比赛。',365730,'I see. I believe you do a report on some of the races.',1,361144),(12019,257,'是的，这是对的。事实上，我们每周都会对每场比赛进行报告，并且总是试图说明这一点。',374110,'Yes that''s right. In fact we do a weekly report on each race and we always try to illustrate it.',1,365739),(12020,257,'好吧，我的朋友真的很喜欢拍照。她刚买了一台新相机。',381350,'OK - well