下车沿着海滨漫步。',124800,'Leaving the aquarium, the bus tour goes along the coast road and after a few kilometres comes to the Old Fishing Villagewhere you can get off to stroll along the waterfront.(Q12)',1,111759),(12036,258,'这里有一些原始建筑，但大部分地区已经现代化，现在被用作各种海上船只的港口，包括游艇和一些令人惊叹的动力艇。',139110,'There are some original buildings here but most of the area has been modernised and is now used as a harbour for all kinds of sea craft including yachts and some amazing power boats.',1,124804),(12037,258,'然后游览前往最后一站，这是大多数商店所在的地方。',145760,'The tour then heads off to the last stop and this is where most of the shops are.',1,139114),(12038,258,'因此，对于那些热衷于购物的人来说，这是适合您的地方。',151850,'So for those of you keen to do a bit of shoppingthis is the place for you.(Q13)',1,145766),(12039,258,'我们的建议是早上比较安静的时候去镇上的这个地方。',158600,'Our advice is to go to this part of the town in the morning when it is relatively quiet.',1,151856),(12040,258,'下午确实很忙，尤其是在旺季。',164710,'It does get very busy in the afternoons, especially at the height of the season.',1,158605),(12041,258,'镇上的这一地区有一座古老的喷泉，许多人喜欢在那里拍照，所以请注意这一点。',218370,'This area of the town includes an ancient water fountain where many people like to have their photograph taken 一 so do look out for this.(Q14)',1,164713),(12042,258,'现在是成本和时间安排的一些细节。',223310,'Now some details of the costs and timings.',1,218371),(12043,258,'包括两名成人和最多三名儿童的家庭票价格为 30 英镑。',230660,'A family ticket, which includes two adults and up to three children, costs £30.',1,223313),(12044,258,'成人票 15 英镑，15 岁以下儿童 5 英镑，学生票 10 英镑，只要您有学生证。',243630,'An adult ticket costs £15, children under the age of fifteen are £5 and student tickets are £10 as long as you have a student card.(Q15)',1,230664),(12045,258,'所有车票的有效期为 24 小时，这意味着您可以在 24 小时内随意上下车。',255050,'All tickets are valid for 24 hours, which means that you can get on and off the bus as many times as you like within a 24-hour period.',1,243636),(12046,258,'例如，您可以在下午开始游览并在第二天早上完成。',262700,'So you could, for example, start the tour in the afternoon and complete it the following morning.',1,255053),(12047,258,'当天的第一班巴士在上午 10 点离开车站，最后一班巴士在下午 6 点离开。',271570,'The first bus of the day leaves the station at 10 am and the last one of the day leaves at 6 pm.',1,262703),(12048,258,'公共汽车每三十分钟一班，每次游览总共需要五十分钟。',278710,'Buses leave every thirty minutes and each tour takes a total of fifty minutes.(Q16)',1,271571),(12049,258,'每一站都有很多景点，所以无论您在哪里下车，都会有很多事情要做。',287070,'There are many attractions at each of the stops, so wherever you get off the bus there will be plenty to do.',1,278718),(12050,258,'除了位于水族馆附近的博物馆外，巴士旅游门票不包括任何这些景点的入口。',297390,'The bus tour tickets do not include entrance to any of these attractions apart from the museum which is located near the aquarium.(Q17)',1,287076),(12051,258,'一些巴士有当地导游，他们会指出名胜古迹并提供有关城镇的信息。',305720,'Some buses have local guides, who will point out places of interest and will provide information on the town.',1,297399),(12052,258,'但是，我们不能保证每辆巴士都有导游，所以我们也有旅游局专门为巴士之旅录制的音频解说。',318670,'However, we cannot guarantee that every bus will have a guide and so we also have an audio commentary that has been specially recorded for the bus tour by the tourist office.(Q18)',1,305728),(12053,258,'巴士上提供耳机，这些耳机很容易操作。',324370,'Headphones are available on the bus and these are easy to operate.',1,318671),(12054,258,'这些没有额外费用 - 只需插入，选择所需的语言并调整音量。',332320,'There is no extra charge for these - just plug in, select the required language and adjust the volume.',1,324372),(12055,258,'由于 Pacton-on-Sea 的冬季月份相当寒冷和潮湿，巴士之旅仅在 3 月至 9 月期间运营。',341670,'Due to the winter months being rather cold and wet in Pacton- on-Sea, the bus tours only operate from March to September.',1,332321),(12056,258,'在这几个月里，天气通常温暖而阳光充足，所以记得带上一些防晒用品，尤其是在炎热的天气里。',350910,'The weather is usually warm and sunny during these months so remember to bring some sun protection, especially on hot days.',1,341676),(12057,258,'当然，夏天这里偶尔会下雨，所以如果天气不好，记得带一些雨衣。',359760,'And of course, it does occasionally rain here in the summer so if the weather looks bad, remember to bring some rainwear.(Q19)',1,350917),(12058,258,'无论天气如何，都可以乘坐巴士游览。',364390,'The bus tours are available no matter what the weather.',1,359768),(12059,258,'在夏季的高峰期，旅游会非常繁忙，因此建议您预订。”',370430,'At the height of the summer the tours can get very busy so you are advised to book.',1,364397),(12060,258,'您可以在线、通过电话、车站和任何其他旅游站点预订车票。',379610,'You can book tickets online, over the phone and also at the station and at any of the other tour stops.',1,370437),(12061,258,'通过电话预订时，您可以在旅行开始时在任何站点取票。',386890,'When booking over the phone you can collect your tickets at any of the stops at the start of your tour.',1,379611),(12062,258,'当您在线完成时，您可以打印您必须记得随身携带的电子机票。',393020,'When you do it online you can print your e-ticket which you must remember to bring with you.(Q20)',1,386896),(12063,258,'感谢您拨打 Pacton-on-Sea 电话热线，我们期待很快在我们的一辆旅游巴士上见到您。',400770,'Thank you for calling the Pacton-on-Sea phoneline and we look forward to seeing you soon on one of our tour buses.',1,393023),(12064,259,'你好，我是技术部的兰迪尔·戈特拉。',47220,'Hello 一 I’m Randhir Ghotra from the technologies department.',1,43358),(12065,259,'是啊。好的。我是戴夫·哈德利。谢谢你来看我。',52440,'Ah yes. Good. I''m Dave Hadley. Thanks for coming to see me.',1,47229),(12066,259,'没关系。我相信您希望我们为您做一些工作？',56210,'That''s OK. I believe you want us to do some work for you?',1,52445),(12067,259,'是的，这是对的。嗯，我负责大学的学生招生，我使用计算机系统来帮助处理学生注册和安排时间表。但它确实不适合我们这些天的工作方式。十多年了，刚推出的时候还不错，现在还不够好。',84710,'Yes that''s right. Um, I''m responsible for student admissions to the college and I use a computer system to help process student enrolments and to do the timetabling. But it really doesn''t suit the way we work these days. It''s over ten years old and although it was fine when it was first introduced, it is just not good enough now.(Q21)',1,56211),(12068,259,'好的 一你遇到什么问题？',88000,'OK 一 what problems are you experiencing?',1,84714),(12069,259,'嗯，20 年前，学院很小，我们没有现在的学生或导师。',97640,'Well, 20 years ago, the college was quite small and we didn''t have the numbers of students or tutors that we have now.',1,88000),(12070,259,'所以系统无法处理不断增加的交易量......',101230,'So the system can''t handle the increasing volumes ...',1,97643),(12071,259,'好吧，现在有更多的数据，有时系统似乎已经崩溃，但事实上，从一个屏幕转到下一个屏幕只需要很长时间。',113090,'Well, there''s a lot more data now and it sometimes seems the system has crashed but, in fact, it just takes ages to go from one screen to the next.(Q22)',1,101237),(12072,259,'没错。这是唯一的问题吗？',115950,'Right. Is that the only problem?',1,113097),(12073,259,'嗯，这是主要的，但还有其他的。过去，制定时间表非常简单，但现在我们有更多的课程，而让事情变得复杂的是很多课程都有选择。',132480,'Well that’s the main one, but there are others. In the past, doing the timetabling was quite simple but now we have a lot more courses and what''s made it complicated is that many of them have options.(Q23)',1,115951),(12074,259,'是的，但是这个系统应该能让你把不同的选择包括在内。',136190,'Right - but the system should allow you to include those.',1,132488),(12075,259,'不，它没有。它应该 - 几年前我们确实要求技术部门的人修复它，但他们似乎从来没有时间。',150010,'Well no, it doesn''t. It was supposed to - and a few years ago we did ask someone from the technologies department to fix it, but they never seemed to have the time.',1,136199),(12076,259,'嗯……系统还有其他问题吗？',153510,'Hmm ... are there any other issues with the system?',1,150011),(12077,259,'好吧——我还有其它任务在身，所以我制作时间表的时间就更少了。 兰迪尔，如果您能做些什么来提高流程效率，那将非常有帮助。',169670,'Well - I’ve been given extra responsibilities and so I have even less time to do the timetabling. If there was anything you could do, Randhir, to make the process more efficient, that would be really helpful.',1,153511),(12078,259,'听起来你需要一位助手，显然这不可能，那建一个网上系统，学生能用来自己做时间表，怎么样？',180910,'Well it sounds like you could do with an assistant but that''s obviously not possible, so what about having an online system that students can use to do their scheduling?',1,169670),(12079,259,'那将如何运作？',182550,'How would that work?',1,180914),(12080,259,'嗯 - 这可能意味着学生的选择更少，但我们可以创建所有课程和选项的固定时间表，然后他们可以查看可用的内容......',194130,'Well - it may mean less choice for students but we could create a fixed schedule of all the courses and options and they could then view what was available ...',1,182554),(12081,259,'......并为自己解决 - 这听起来很棒。',197790,'... and work it out for themselves 一 that sounds great.(Q24)',1,194132),(12082,259,'好的，所以……嗯……我们需要决定是改进现有系统还是建立一个全新的系统。',206770,'OK, so ... um ... we''ll need to decide whether or not to improve the existing system or to build a completely new system.',1,197798),(12083,259,'好吧，我更愿意拥有一个新系统。坦率地说，我已经受够了旧的。',213370,'Well I''d much prefer to have a new system. Quite frankly, I’ve had enough of the old one.',1,206774),(12084,259,'好的——虽然从长远来看它可能会为你省钱，但这可能需要更长的时间。你希望什么时候实现这个功能？',221700,'OK 一 that''ll probably take longer although it may save you money in the long run. When were you hoping to have this in place?(Q25)',1,213377),(12085,259,'嗯，现在是一月份，新入学的学生将在九月份。我们真的需要在接下来的几周内开始处理入学申请。',235690,'Well it''s January now and the new intake of students will be in September. We need to start processing admissions 一 in the next few weeks really.',1,221704),(12086,259,'恐怕需要几个星期以上的时间。作为初步估计，我认为我们将在 4 月或 5 月改进现有系统，但对于新系统，至少需要 9 个月。那最早是十月。',278860,'Well it will take more than a few weeks, I''m afraid. As an initial estimate I think we’ll be looking at April or May to improve the existing system but for a new system it would take at least nine months. That would be October at the earliest.(A26)',1,235698),(12087,259,'如果我们要拥有一个新系统，下一步是什么？',284520,'What are the next steps if we are to have a new system?',1,278866),(12088,259,'那么，第一个问题是——你有高层的支持吗？',289550,'Well, the first question is 一 do you have support from your senior management?(Q27)',1,284528),(12089,259,'是的，我已经和他们讨论过了，他们也很想完成这项工作。',295190,'Yes, I''ve already discussed it with them and they''re also keen to get this work done.',1,289559),(12090,259,'好的，因为我要说的是，这是您需要做的第一件事，否则我们将无法继续。',302930,'OK, because I was going to say, that''s the first thing you need to do and without that we can''t go ahead.',1,295199),(12091,259,'是的，我已经做到了。',304620,'Yes, I''ve done that.',1,302931),(12092,259,'那挺好的。',305500,'That''s good.',1,304626),(12093,259,'实际上，他们提