ast week or so.(Q27)',1,254416),(12239,263,'嗯，那很好。我唯一真正与之交谈过的人是我的导师。他非常平易近人，似乎明白开始上大学有多么困难。',282390,'Well, that''s good. The only person I’ve spoken to really is my tutor. He''s very approachable and seems to understand how difficult it can be starting university.',1,268744),(12240,263,'有一个可以交谈的人是件好事。他可能会帮助你认识其他学生。',288890,'It''s good to have someone you can talk to. And he may help you meet other students.',1,282391),(12241,263,'其实这并不困扰我。我迟早会认识一些人。更多的是找出我需要做什么，去哪里等等的问题。我希望他能帮助我。',304060,'Actually that doesn''t bother me. I''m bound to get to know some people sooner or later. It''s more a question of finding out what I need to do, where to go and so on. I hope he can help me with that.(Q28)',1,288891),(12242,263,'哦，我会这么想的。好吧，我们当然还有很多工作要做。看上去可真漫长啊，对吧，要学三年呢。',315130,'Oh I would have thought so. Well we certainly have a lot of work ahead of us. It seems like a long time, doesn''t it? Started for 3 years',1,304069),(12243,263,'是的，它确实如此——但我相信它会很快过去。你知道我真的很害怕第一次评估。',323180,'Yes it does - but I''m sure it''ll go quickly. You know I''m really dreading the first assessment.',1,315135),(12244,263,'是的，对于我正在做的课程，我们必须在下个月底交出我们的第一个课程。',329820,'Yes 一 for the course I''m doing we have to hand our first one in at the end of next month.(Q29)',1,323185),(12245,263,'真的一那么你有话题了吗？',333670,'Really 一 so have you got the topic yet?',1,329826),(12246,263,'没有，但我们很快就会得到它。 我 还不确定我们要写多少——我希望不要写太多！',341670,'No 一 but we''ll get it soon. I’m not sure how much we have to write yet - not too much, I hope!',1,333678),(12247,263,'我明白你的意思。而且很难学习，尤其是我现在所在的地方。',347360,'I know what you mean. And it''s hard to study especially where I am now.',1,341678),(12248,263,'哦，你住在哪里？',349870,'Oh 一 where are you living?',1,347365),(12249,263,'我住在宿舍楼里。我认为这将是一个好主意，因为周围会有很多人，但我发现它有点吵。我可以看到，当我真的需要开始工作时，我会遇到问题。',366990,'I''m living in a hall of residence. I thought that would be a good idea as there''d be a lot of people around but I‘m finding it a bit noisy. I can see that I''m going to have problems when I really need to